hadiths[324]{hadithnumber,text}:
837,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne kaha : jab musalman Madina aaey to wo ikatthey ho jatey aur namazon ke oqaat ka intizar kartey, koi iska elaan nahi karta tha. aik din unhon-ne iske barey mein guftgu ki to kuchh ne kaha : esaiyon ke ghantey ki tarah aik ghantaa ley lo aur kuchh ne kaha : yahood ke Qarna jaisa Qarna, albatta Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum aik aadmi hi kyon nahi bhej detey jo Namaz ka elaan karey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Bilal ! utho aur Namaz ka elaan karo."
838,"Khalaf bin Hisham ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hadis sunai, neez Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : hamein Ismail bin-Ulaih ne khabar di, un donon ( Hammad aur Yahya ( ne Khalid Haza se, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ko hukm diya gaya ke wo azan dohraaein aur iqamat ikehri kahin . Yahya ne ibne-Ulaih se ( bayan ki hui ( apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya : main (Ismail ( ne ye riwayat Ayub ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : ( azan dohraaein ( iqamat ke siwa ."
839,"Abdul Wahab Saqafi ne Khalid Haza se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke unhon-ne ( sahaba ( ne (us par) baat ki ke kisi aisi cheez ke zariey se Namaz ke waqt ki alamat muqarrar karein jis ko log pehchan liya karein. unhon-ne kaha ke wo aag roshan karein ya naaqoos ( ghanti ( bajaaein , phir ( aakhir kaar ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya gaya ke wo dohri azan aur ikehri iqamat kahin ."
840,"Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Khalid Haza ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki ke jab log zyada ho gaey to unhon-ne guftgu ki ke wo alamat muqarrar karein. . . . aagey ( Abdul Wahab) Saqafi ki hadis ki tarah hai, farq sirf itna hai ke us ( Wuhaib ( ne (aag roshan karein, ki jagah) aag jalaaein, kaha."
841,"Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya gaya ke dohri azan aur ikehri iqamat kahin ."
842,"Abu-Ghassan Mismai aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( Abu-Ghassan ne kaha : hamein Muaz ne hadis sunai aur Ishaq ne kaha : hamein Hisham Dastuwai ke betey Muaz ne khabar di, unhon ( Muaz ( ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Aamir ahwal se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Mahzura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ye azan sikhai : (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ، أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ، أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله ، أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله ) , phir 2 baara kaha : ( أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ( , 2 baar , (أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله‏) , 2 baar (حی على الصلوٰة ) aur (حي على الفلاح) 2 baar . Ishaq ne ye izafa kya : (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، لا إله إلا الله)"
843,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke 2 muazzan they, Bilal aur naa-beenaa ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ."
844,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bhi usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki gaee hai.
845,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ibn-Umme-Maktoom Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye azan diya kartey they, halanke wo naa-beenaa they."
846,Yahya bin-Abdullah aur Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath us ( uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ( ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
847,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( dushman par) tuloo fajr ke waqt hamla kartey they aur azan ki awaz par kaan lagaey rakhtey they, phir agar azan sun letey to ruk jatey warna hamla kar detey, ( aisa hua ke) aap ne aik aadmi ko kehtey huey suna : ( Allahu-akbar Allahu-akbar ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : fitrat (Islam) par hai. phir usne kaha : ( أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله , أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to aag se nikal gaya. is par sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha to wo bakriyon ka charwaha tha."
848,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum azan suno to jo muazzan kehta hai usi ki tarah kaho.
849,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko suna, aap farma rahe they : jab tum muazzan ko suno to isi tarah kaho jaisey wo kehta hai, phir mujh par durood bhejo kyonke jo mujh par aik baar durood bhejta hai, Allah Taala iske badley main is par das rahmatein nazil farmata hai, phir Allah Taala se mere liye waseela maango kyonke wo jannat mein aik maqam hai jo Allah ke bandon mein se sirf aik bandey ko milega aur mujhey ummeed hai wo mein hunga , chunanche jisne mere liye waseela talab kya uske liye ( meri ( shafaat wajib ho gaee."
850,"Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab muazzan ( Allaahu-akbar, Allahu-akbar ( kahey to tum mein se (har ( aik ( Allahu-akbar Allahu-akbar ( kahey , phir wo ( muazzan ( kahey ( أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله) to wo bhi kahey : ( أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله ( phir ( muazzan ( (أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله) kahey to wo bhi (أشهد أن محمدا رسول الله‏) kahey , phir wo ( muazzan ( (حی على الصلوٰة) kahey to wo (لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله ) kahey , phir muazzan ( حي على الفلاح) kahey , to wo (لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله ) kahey , phir ( muazzan ( ) Allahu-akbar Allahu-akbar ( kahey , to wo bhi) Allahu-akbar Allahu-akbar ( kahey , phir ( muazzan ( ) لا إله إلا الله ( kahey to wo bhi apne dil se ( لا إله إلا الله ( kahey to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga."
851,"Muhammad-bin Rumeh aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ki 2 alag alag sanadon se Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Rasulullah se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jisne muazzan ki awaz suntey huey ye kaha : أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, wo akelaa hai, uska koi Sharik nahi. وأن محمدا عبده ورسوله aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske bandey aur rasool hain. (رضيت بالله ربا وبمحمد رسولا وبالإسلام دينا) main Allah ke rab honey par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rasool honey par aur Islam ke Deen honey par razi hun. to uske gunah bakhsh diye jaengey. ibne- Rumeh ne apni riwayat mein kaha : jisne muazzan ki awaz suntey huey ye kaha : ( وأنا أشهد (aur Quteba ne ( وأنا (ka lafz bayan nahi kya."
852,"Abda ne Talha bin Yahya (bin Talha bin Ubaidullah ( se aur unhon-ne apne chacha (Eisaa bin Talha bin Ubaidullah ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha, unke paas muazzan unhein Namaz ke liye bulaney aaya. to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : qiyamat ke din muazzan , logon mein sabse zyada lambi gardanon waley hongey. ,"
853,"Sufiyan ne Talha bin Yahya se aur unhon-ne (apne chacha ( Esa-bin-Talha se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : . . . . . . . . . .) aagey ( pichhli riwayat ki manind (tarah) hai."
854,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan ( Talha bin Naafe ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : bila shubah shaitan jab Namaz ki pukar ( azan ( sunta hai to ( bhag kar) chala jata hai yahan tak ke Roha ke maqam par pahunch jata hai. Sulaiman (Aamash) ne kaha : maine un (apne ustad abu Sufiyan Talha bin Naafe) se Roha ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : ye Madina se chhatein mail (ke faasley ( par hai."
855,abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki.
856,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shaitan jab Namaz ke liye pukar (ki awaz ( sunta hai to gooz maarta hua bhaagta hai taake muazzan ki awaz na sun sakey, phir jab muazzan khamosh ho jata hai to wapas aata hai aur) namaziyon ke dilon mein) waswasa paida karta hai, phir jab iqamat sunta hai to chala jata hai taake uski awaz na suney , phir jab wo khamosh ho jata hai to wapas aata hai aur) logon ke dilon mein) waswasa daalta hai."
857,"Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh as-Saman) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab muazzan azan kehta hai to shaitan peeth pher kar gooz maarta hua jata hai."
858,"Rooh ne Suhel se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere walid ne mujhey banu- Harisa ki taraf bheja kaha : mere sath hamara aik ladka ( khaadim ya hamara aik sathi bhi tha) usko kisi awaz dene waley ne baagh se iska naam lekar awaz di. kaha : jo ( ladka ( mere sath tha us ne baagh ke andar jhanka to usey kuchh nazar na aaya, chunanche maine ye ( waqia ( apne walid ko bataya to unhon-ne kaha : agar mujhey malum hota ke tumko wo waqia pes aaeyga to main tumhen na bhejta lekin) aainda ( tum agar koi awaz suno to Namaz ki azan do kyonke maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey they ke aap ne farmaya : jab Namaz ke liye pukara jata hai to shaitan peeth pher kar gooz maarta hua bhag jata hai."
859,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke bila shubah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Namaz ke liye azan di jati hai to shaitan gooz maarta hua peechhey bhag jata hai taake azan na suney , chunanche jab azan poori kar di jati hai to aa jata hai yahan tak ke jab Namaz ke liye takbeer kahi jati hai to ( phir ( peeth pher kar bhag jata hai, yahan tak ke jab takbeer khatm ho jati hai to aa jata hai taake insan ke dil mein waswasa daley . usey kehta hai : falan cheez ko yad karo, falan cheez ko yad karo, wo cheezein jo usey pahley yad nahi hotin, yahan tak ke aadmi ki ye haalat ho jati hai ke usko pata hi nahi chalta us ne kitni Namaz padhi hai."
860,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ki tarah bayan kya, magar unhon-ne ( ما يدري كم صلى  ke bajaey) (إن يدري كيف صلى) wo nahi janta kaisey Namaz padhi, kaha."
861,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha : jab aap Namaz shuru kartey to apne donon hath uthatey yahan tak ke unhein kandhon ke barabar ley aatey aur rukoo se pahley aur (is waqt bhi) jab rukoo se sar uthatey . aap 2 sajdon ke darmyan unhein na uthatey they."
862,"ibne-Juraij ne ibne-Shahab se aur unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to apne donon hath buland kartey yahan tak ke aap ke kandhon ke samney aa jatey, phir Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir jab rukoo karna chahtey to yahi kartey aur jab rukoo se sar uthatey to bhi aisa kartey aur jab sajdey se apna sar uthatey to aisa na kartey they."
863,"Aqeel aur Yunus donon ne isi tarah riwayat ki jis tarah ibne-Juraij ne ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to donon hath uthatey , phir takbeer kehtey. ( unhon-ne ( بحذو منكبيه (ke bajaey ( حذو منكبيه ( kaha, donon ka mafhoom aik hai.)"
864,"abu-Qilaba se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, jab wo Namaz padhtey to Allahu-akbar kehtey phir apne donon hath uthatey aur jab rukoo karna chahtey to apne donon hath uthatey aur jab rukoo se apna sar uthatey to apne donon hath uthatey aur unhon-ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisa hi kya kartey they."
865,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Nasar bin Aasim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Allahu-akbar kehtey to apne donon hath buland kartey yahan tak ke unhein apne kanon ke barabar ley jatey aur jab rukoo kartey to ( phir ( apne donon hath buland kartey yahan tak ke unhein apne kanon ke barabar ley jatey aur jab rukoo se apna sar uthatey to ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey aur aisa hi kartey."
866,Qatada se ( abu-Awana ke bajaey) Saeed ne baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke unhon ( Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ( ne Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aur) Saeed ne) kaha : yahan tak ke donon hath apne donon kanon ke kinaron ke samney ley jatey.
867,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) unhein Namaz padha rahe they, to jab bhi wo jhuktey aur) sar aur jism ko uper ( uthatey to Allahu-akbar kehtey, phir jab salam phera to kaha : Allah ki qism ! main Namaz main tum sab ki nisbat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada mushabihat (similarity) rakhta hun."
868,"hamein ibne-Juraij ne khabar di kaha : mujhey ibne-Shahab ne Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to khadey hotey huey takbeer kehtey, phir rukoo kartey huey takbeer kehtey, phir jab rukoo se kamar uthatey to ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey, phir qiyam ki haalat main ( ربنا ولك الحمد ( kehtey, phir jab sajda karne ke liye jhuktey to takbeer kehtey, phir jab apna sar uthatey to takbeer kehtey, phir ( doosra ( sajda kartey waqt takbeer kehtey, phir jab ( sajdey se) apna sar uthatey to takbeer kehtey, aap poori Namaz mein isi tarah kartey yahan tak ke usko mukammal kar letey aur jab 2 rakaton se baithney ke baad uthtey to (is waqt bhi) takbeer kehtey. phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey : main Namaz main tum sab ki nisbat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath zyada mushabeh (similar) hun."
869,"Aqeel ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Haris ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz ke liye khadey hotey to khadey hotey waqt takbeer kehtey. . . . . . aagey ibne-Juraij ki hadis ki tarah hai aur) Aqeel ne) Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye qaul ke main Namaz main tum sab ki nisbat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada mushabeh (similar) hon, bayan nahi kya."
870,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab Marwan Madina mein apna naaib bana kar jata to jab wo farz Namaz ke liye khadey hotey , takbeer kehtey. . . . . . . iske baad) Yunus ne) ibne-Juraij ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya. un ( Yunus ( ki hadis mein (ye izafa ( hai ke jab wo Namaz poori kar letey aur salam phertey to masjid walon ki taraf munh kartey (aur ( kehtey is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! main Namaz main tum sabse zyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mushabeh (similar) hun."
871,"Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne abu-Salma se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz mein jab bhi) sar ( uthatey aur jhukatey , takbeer kehtey, is par ham ne kaha : Abu-Hurera ! ye takbeer kya hai? unhon-ne kaha : yaqinan yahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz hai."
872,Suhel ke walid Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo jab bhi (namaz mein sar ( jhukatey aur uthatey to takbeer kehtey aur batatey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisa hi kya kartey they.
873,"Mutarrif se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine aur Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhi. jab wo sajda kartey to takbeer kehtey aur jab apna sar uthatey to takbeer kehtey aur jab 2 rakaton ke baad khadey hotey to takbeer kehtey, jab ham Namaz se farigh huey to Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne mera hath pakda , phir kaha : unhon-ne hamein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz padhai hai ya kaha : unhon-ne mujhey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz yad dila di hai."
874,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne ibne-Shahab Zohri se, unhon-ne Mehmood-bin Rabe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo is baat ki nisbat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf kartey they (ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (us shakhs ki koi Namaz nahi jisne fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) na padhi."
875,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Mehmood-bin Rabe ne Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is shakhs ki koi Namaz nahi jisne Ummul-Quran ( Fatiha ( nahi padhi."
876,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Mehmood-bin Rabe (Raziallahu anhu) ne, jinke chehrey par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke kuwein se kulli karke pani ka chhinta diya tha, unhein bataya ke Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Ummul-Quran ki qirat na ki, uski koi Namaz nahi."
877,Zohri ke aik aur shagird Mamar ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur ye izafa kya : ( Fatiha (aur uske baad) Quran ka kuchh hissey .)
878,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jisne koi Namaz padhi aur is mein Umme- ul-Quraa ki qirat na ki to naaqis hai. teen martaba farmaya, yani poori hi nahi. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya : ham imam ke peechhey hotey hain. unhon-ne kaha : usko apne dil mein padh lo kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : Allah Taala ne farmaya : maine Namaz apne aur apne bandey ke darmyan aadhi aadhi taqseem ki hai aur mere bandey ne jo maanga , uska hai. jab banda ( الحمد لله رب العالمين ( sab tareef Allah hi ke liye jo jahaanon ka rab hai. kehta hai to Allah Taala farmata hai : mere bandey ne meri tareef ki. aur jab wo kehta hai : ( الرحمن الرحيم ( sabse zyada raham karne wala hamesha meherbani karne wala. , to Allah Taala farmata hai : mere bandey ne meri sana bayan ki. phir jab wo kehta hai : (مالك يوم الدين) jazaa ke din ka Malik. , to ( Allah ( farmata hai : mere bandey ne meri buzurgi bayan ki. aur aik baar farmaya : mere bandey ne (apne maamlaat ( mere sipurd kar diye. phir jab wo kehta hai : ( إياك نعبد وإياك نستعين ( ham teri hi bandagi kartey aur tujh hi se madad chahtey hain. to ( Allah ( farmata hai : ye ( hissey ( mere aur mere bandey ke darmyan hai aur mere bandey ne jo maanga , iska hai aur jab wo kehta hai : (إهدنا الصراط المستقيم صراط الذين أنعمت عليهم غير المغضوب عليهم والا الضالين) hamein seedha raasta dikha, un logon ka raasta jin par tu ney inaam farmaya, na ghazab kiye gaey logon ki ho aur na gumrahon ka. to ( Allah ( farmata hai : ye mere bandey ke liye hai aur mere bandey ka hai jo usney maanga . Sufiyan ne kaha : mujhey ye riwayat Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob ne sunai, mein unke paas gaya, wo ghar mein bimar they. maine unse us hadis ke barey mein sawal kya (to unhon-ne mujhey ye hadis sunai. ("
879,"Malik-bin-Anas ne Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hishaam-bin-Zohra ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Saaib se suna, kehtey they : maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, (jis tarah pichhli riwayat hai.)"
880,"ibne-Juraij ne bataya ke hamein Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin Hishaam-bin-Zohra ke beton ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Saaib ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne koi Namaz padhi aur is mein Ummul-Quran na padhi, , . . . aagey Sufiyan ki hadis ki tarah hai aur) Malik-bin-Anas aur ibne-Juraij ( donon ki riwayat mein hai : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne farmaya : maine Namaz apne aur apne bandey ke darmyan aadhi aadhi taqseem ki hai, iska aadha hissey mere liye hai aur aadha mere bandey ke liye."
881,"abu-Ovais ne kaha : mujhey Alaa ne khabar di, kaha : maine apne walid se aur abu-Saaib se suna, wo donon Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke saathi they, un donon ne kaha ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne koi Namaz ada ki aur is mein fatihatul-kitab (Sura Fatiha) na padhi to wo (namaz ( adhoori hai. aap ne teen baar ye jumla farmaya, . . . aagey uper zikr ki gaee asaatza ( Malik , Sufiyan , ibne-Juraij ( ki hadis ki tarah hai"
882,"Habib bin Shahid se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Ata se suna, wo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qirat ke baghair koi Namaz nahi. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jo (namaz ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey liye unchi qirat se ada ki ham ne bhi tumharey liye wo unchi qirat se ada ki aur jis (namaz ( mein aap ne ( qirat ko) makhfi rakha , ham ne bhi usey tumharey liye makhfi rakha."
883,"ibne-Juraij ne Ata se khabar di, kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (namaz padhney wala ( poori Namaz main (har rakaat mein) qirat kare. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo ( qirat ( hamein ( buland awaz se) sunai, ham ne bhi tumhen sunai aur jo aap ne ham se ( awaz aahista karke ( makhfi rakhi ham ne usey tum se makhfi rakha. aik aadmi ne unse kaha : agar main Ummul-Quran se zyada na padhun ? to unhon-ne kaha : agar us se zyada padho to behtar hai aur agar us ( Fatiha ( par ruk jao to wo tumhen kifaayat karegi ."
884,"Habib muallim se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Ata se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : har Namaz mein qirat hai. to jo ( qirat ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein sunai ham ne tumhen sunai aur jo unhon-ne ham se posheeda rakhi , ham ne wo tum se posheeda rakhi aur jisne Ummul-Kitab padh li to uske liye wo kafi hai aur jisne (is se) zayed padha to wo behtar hai."
885,"saiyedna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif farma they itney mein aik aadmi aaya us ne Namaz padhney ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam ka jawab de kar farmaya : jao Namaz padho tum ne Namaz nahi padhi. '' to usne wapas ho kar pahley ki tarah Namaz padhi aur lot kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne w'alaikumassalaam kehtey huey farmaya : '' jao Namaz padho tum ne Namaz ada nahi ki.'' chunanche isi tarah wo Namaz padhta aur lot kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam karta aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yahi farmatey : '' jao Namaz padho tum ne ada nahi ki.'' aakhir us shakhs ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! qism hai us zaat ki jisne aapko bar-haq banaya hai, main us se zyada achchhey tareeqey ke ilawa mazeed kisi cheez se nawaqif hun. baraahe-karam aap hi mujhey bata dijiye ? to irshad hua : ''tum jab Namaz ke liye khadey ho to pahley Allahu-akbar kaho aur phir jitna Quran Karim tum baa-aasaanii padh saktey ho wo padho iske baad rukoo karo aur phir baa-aaraam bilkul seedhey khadey ho jao aur uske baad ba itminan sajda karo aur phir ba itminan Qada mein baitho aur isi tarah apni poori Namaz mein kya karo."
886,"abu-Usama aur Aabdullah bin Numer ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Saeed bin abi Saeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi ne masjid mein dakhil ho kar Namaz padhi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik taraf ( tashrif farma ( they. . . . . . phir donon ne usi waqiey ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki aur) hadis ke hissey ( mein un donon ne ye izafa kya : jab tum Namaz ke liye khadey ho to khub achi tarah wuzu karo, phir qibley ki taraf rukh karo, phir takbeer kaho."
887,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Zarara-bin-Ufa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Zohar ya Asr ki Namaz padhai , phir farmaya : tum mein se kis ne mere peechhey ( سبح اسم ربك الأعلى‏ ( padhi ? to aik aadmi ne kaha : maine , aur khair ke siwa us se main aur kuchh nahi chahta tha. aap ne farmaya : mujhey ilm ho gaya ke tum mein se koi mujhey us (yani qirat ( mein uljha raha hai."
888,"Shoba ne Qatada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Zarara-bin-Ufa se suna, wo Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz padhi to aik aadmi ne aap ke peechhey ( سبح اسم ربك الأعلى‏ ( padhni shuru kar di. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to farmaya : tum mein se kis ne padha , ya ( farmaya : ( tum mein se padhney wala kon hai? aik aadmi ne kaha : main hun. aap ne farmaya : main samjha ke tum mein se koi mujhey usmein uljhaa raha hai"
889,Qatada ke aik aur shagird ibne-abi-Aruba ne isi sanad ke sath ( uper zikr ki gaee ( riwayat bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz padhai aur farmaya : main jaan gaya ke tum mein se koi mujhey usmein uljhaa raha hai.
890,"ham se Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, kaha : maine Qatada ko Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey suna, kaha : maine Rasulullah (sl), Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Namaz padhi, maine unmein se kisi ko  بسم اللہ الرحمن الرحیم padhtey nahi suna."
891,"Muhammad-bin ( Jafar ke bajaey) Abu-Dawud ne Shoba se isi sanad se riwayat ki aur ye izafa kya ke Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada se kaha : kya aap ne ye riwayat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suni hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan , ham ne unse iske barey mein puchha tha."
892,"Auzai ne Abda se riwayat ki ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ye kalimaat buland awaz se padhtey they : ( سبحانك اللهم ! وبحمدك , تبارك اسمك وتعالى جدك , wla إله غيرك (aey Allah ! to apni hamd ke sath paak hai. tera naam bada ba-barkat hai aur teri azmat w shaan badi buland hai aur terey siwa koi maabud nahi. ( neez Auzai hi ki) Qatada (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se (apni ( riwayat ki khabar detey huey un ( Auzai ( ki taraf likh bheja ke unhon-ne ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Qatada ko hadis sunai, kaha : maine Nabi (sl), Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey Namaz padhi hai, wo (namaz ka ( shuruat ( الحمد لله رب العالمين ( se kartey they, wo ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( ) buland awaz se) nahi kehtey they, na qirat ke shuru main aur na iske aakhir main hi (doosri sura ke shuruat par. ("
893,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne bataya ke unhon-ne Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo yahi (pichhli ( hadis bayan kartey they."
894,"Ali-bin Hujr Sadi aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne (alfaz unhi ke hain) Ali-bin-Mus-hir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Mukhtar-bin-fulful se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey darmyan they jab usi beech mein aap kuchh der ke liye neend jaisi kaifiyat mein chaley gaey, phir aap ne muskuratey huey apna sar uthaya to ham ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap kis baat par hansey ? aap ne farmaya : abhi mujh par aik sura nazil ki gaee hai. phir aap ne padha : ( بِسْمِ اللَّـهِ الرَّحْمَـٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ۝ إِنَّا أَعْطَيْنَاكَ الْكَوْثَرَ۝ فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَانْحَرْ۝ إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ الْأَبْتَرُ۝ ( bila shubah ham ne aapko kausar ata ki. to aap apne rab ke liye Namaz padhein aur qurbani karein, yaqinan aap ka dushman hi jad kata hai. phir aap ne kaha : kya tum jantey ho kausar kya hai? ham ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool zyada jantey hain. aap ne farmaya : wo aik nehar hai jiska mere rab azz-w-jall ne mujh se wada farmaya hai, is par bahut bhalai hai aur wo aik hauz hai jis par qiyamat ke din meri ummat pani peeney ke liye aaeygi, iske bartan sitaron ki tadaad mein hain. unmein se aik shakhs ko kheench liya jaeyga to main arz karunga : aey mere rab! ye meri ummat se hai. to wo farmaeyga : aap nahi jantey ke unhon-ne aap ke baad kya nai baatein nikalin. ( Ali ( ibne- hujr ne apni hadis mein (ye ( izafa kya : aap masjid mein hamarey darmyan they aur) أحدثوا بعدك ( ki jagah ( ) أحدث بعدك (us ne nai baat nikali kaha."
895,"ibne- Fuzel ne Mukhtar-bin-fulful se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) neend jaisi kaifiyat mein chaley gaey, ( aagey ( jis tarah ibne-Mus-hir ki hadis hai, albatta unhon ( ibne- Fuzel ( ne ye alfaz kahey : aik nehar hai jiska mere rab ne mere sath wada kya hai aur is par aik hauz hai. aur ye nahi kaha : iske bartanon ki tadaad sitaron ke barabar hai."
896,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin Juhada ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Abdul-Jabbar bin Waail ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne Alqama bin Waail aur unke aazad karda ghulam se riwayat ki ke un donon ne unke walid Hazrat Waail bin hujr (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap ne Namaz mein jatey waqt apne donon hath buland kiye, takbeer kahi ( Hammam ne bayan kya : kanon ke barabar buland kiye ( phir apna kapda odh liya ( donon hath kapdey ke andar le gaey ( , phir apna dayan hath baain par rakha , phir jab rukoo karna chaha to apne donon hath kapdey se nikaley , phir unhein buland kya, phir takbeer kahi aur rukoo kya, phir jab ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kaha to apne donon hath buland kiye, phir jab sajda kya to apni donon hatheliyon ke darmyan sajda kya."
897,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Namaz main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey kehtey they : Allah par salam ho, falan par salam ho. ( Bukhari ki riwayat mein Jibreel par Mikaail par salam ho. ( to aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : bila shubah Allah khud salam hai, lihaza jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein baithey to kahey : baqaa w badshahat , ikhtiyar w azmat Allah hi ke liye hai, aur saari duaein aur saari pakeeza cheezein ( bhi usi ke liye hain) , aey Nabi ! aap par salam ho aur Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkatein hun. ham par aur Allah ke nek bandon par salam ho. jab koi shakhs ye ( dua ke) kalimaat kahega to ye aasman w zamin mein Allah ke har nek bandey tak pahunchein gey .) phir kahey : ( mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad iske bandey aur rasool hain, phir jo maangna chahey iska intikhab kar ley."
898,"( Jarir ke bajaey) Shoba ne Mansoor se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki aur unhon ( Shoba ( ne phir jo maangna chahey iska intikhab kar ley , (ke kalimaat ( bayan nahi kiye."
899,"Mansoor ke aik aur shagird Zayda ne unse isi sanad ke sath un donon ( Jarir aur Shoba ( ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, lekin aakhiri kalimaat main ( maashaa) (jo chahey ( ki jagah ( ما أحب ( (jo pasand karey) ke alfaz kahey ."
900,"Aamash ne ( abu-Waail ( Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab ham Namaz main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baithtey they. . . .) aagey ( Mansoor ki hadis ki tarah ( hai) aur kaha : iske baad dua ka intikhab kar ley."
901,"Abdullah-bin Sakhbara ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey tashahud sikhaya , meri hatheli aap ki donon hatheliyon ke darmyan thi, ( bilkul usi tarah) jaisey aap mujhey Qurani sura ki taleem detey they. aur unhon-ne ( ibne- Sakhbara ( ne tashahud isi tarah bayan kya jis tarah pichhli rawiyon ne bayan kya."
902,"Imam Muslim ne Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh bin muhajir ki sanadon se Leis se, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair aur Taaus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein tashahud isi tarah sikhatey jis tarah Quran ki koi sura sikhatey they, chunanche aap farmatey they : baqaa w badshahat , azmat w ikhtiyar aur kasarat khair , saari duaein aur saari pakeeza cheezein Allah hi ke liye hain. aap par salam ho aey Nabi ! aur Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkatein hun. ham par aur Allah ke nek bandon par salam ho. mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain. aur ibne- Rumeh ki riwayat ( السورہ من Quran (ke bajaey) ( کما یعلمنا القرآن) (jis tarah aap Quran sikhatey they) hai."
903,"Abdur-Rehman bin Humaid ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne Taaus ke hawale se Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein tashahud yun sikhatey they jaisey aap hamein Quran ki sura sikhatey they."
904,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Yunus bin Juber se aur unhon-ne Hittan bin-Abdullah Raqashi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath aik Namaz padhi, jab wo Qada (namaz mein tashahud ke liye baithney (ke qareeb they, to logon mein se aik shakhs ne kaha : Namaz ko neki aur zakat ke sath rakha gaya hai? jab abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ne Namaz poori kar li to mudey aur kaha : tum mein se ye ye baat kehney wala kon tha? to sab log maarey haibat ke chup rahe, unhon-ne phir kaha : tum mein se ye ye baat kehney wala kon tha? to log haibat ke maarey phir chup rahe to unhon-ne kaha : aey Hittan ! lagta hai tu ney ye baat kahi ? unhon-ne kaha : maine ye nahi kaha, albatta mujhey dar tha ke aap iske sabab meri sarzanish karengey. to logon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : maine ye baat kahi thi aur maine us se bhalai ke siwa aur kuchh na chaha tha. to abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ne kaha : kya tum nahi jantey ke tumhen apni Namaz mein kaisey kehna chahiye ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein khutba diya, aap ne hamarey liye hamara tariqa waazeh kya aur hamein hamari Namaz sikhai . aap ne farmaya : jab tum Namaz padho to apni safon ko seedha karo, phir tum mein se aik shakhs tumhari imamat kiraaey , jab wo takbeer kahey to tum takbeer kaho aur jab wo (غير المغضوب عليهم والا الضالين) kahey to tum Aameen kaho , Allah tumhari dua qabool farmaeyga . phir jab wo takbeer kahey aur rukoo karey to tum takbeer kaho aur rukoo karo, imam tum se pahley rukoo mein jaeyga aur tum se pahley sar uthaeyga . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to ( muqtadi ki taraf se rukoo mein janey ki) ye (deri) us (deri) ka badal hogi (jo rukoo se sar uthaney mein hogi) aur jab imam ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( اللهم ربنا لك الحمد ( kaho , Allah tumhari ( baat ( sunega, kyonke Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se farmaya hai : Allah ne usey sun liya jisne uski hamd bayan ki aur jab imam takbeer kahey aur sajda karey to tum takbeer kaho aur sajda karo, imam tum se pahley sajda karega aur tum se pahley sar uthaeyga. , phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to ye (deri) us (deri) ka badl hogi aur jab wo Qada mein ho to tumhara pahlaa bol (ye (ho : baqa w badshahat , ikhtiyar w azmat , sab paak cheezein aur saari duaein Allah ke liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par salam aur Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkatein hon. ham par aur Allah ke nek bandon par salam ho. mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske bandey aur rasool hain."
905,"abu-Usama ne Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba se hadis bayan ki, neez Muaz bin Hisham ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, isi tarah Jarir ne Sulaiman Taimi se khabar di, un sab ( ibne-abi-Aruba , Hisham aur Sulaiman ( ne Qatada se usi (pichhli ( hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta Qatada se Sulaiman aur unse Jarir ki bayan ki hui hadis mein ye izafa hai : jab imam padhey to tum ghaur se suno. aur abu-Awana ke shagird kaamil ki hadis ke ilawa unmein se kisi ki hadis mein : izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se farmaya hai : Allah ne usey sun liya jisne uski hamd ki. ke alfaz nahi hain. Abu-Ishaq ne kaha : abu-Nazar ke bhaanjey Abu-Bakar ne us hadis ke mutaalliq baat ki to Imam Muslim ne kaha : aapko Sulaiman se bada Hafiz chahiye ? is par Abu-Bakar ne Imam Muslim se kaha : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ? phir ( Abu-Bakar ne) kaha : wo sahi hai, yani (ye izafa ke) jab imam padhey to tum khamosh raho. Imam Muslim ne ( jawab ke taur par) kaha : wo mere nazdeek bhi sahi hai. to Abu-Bakar ne kaha : aap ne usey yahan kyon na rakha (darj kya) ? (Imam Muslim ne jawab mein) kaha : har wo cheez jo mere nazdeek sahi hai, maine usey yahan nahi rakha. yahan maine sirf un ( hadison ( ko rakha jin (ki sihat ( par unhon ( muhaddeseen ( ne ittifaq kya hai."
906,Qatada ke aik aur shagird Mamar ne isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee hadis riwayat ki aur (apni ( hadis mein kaha : chunanche Allah ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se faisla kar diya : (ke ( Allah ne usey sun liya jisne uski hamd bayan ki) qaal (ke bajaey ( qaza (ka lafz riwayat kya. (
907,"Nuaim-bin-Abdullah-Mujmir se riwayat hai ke Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Zaid Ansari ne ( Muhammad ke walid Abdullah-bin-Zaid ye wahi hain jinko Namaz ke liye azan khuwab mein dikhai gaee thi) unhein abu Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq bataya ke unhon-ne kaha : ham Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laaey, chunanche Bashir bin Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se kaha : Allah ke rasool! Allah Taala ne hamein aap par durood bhejney ka hukm diya hai to ham aap par durood kaisey bhejein? unhon-ne kaha : is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey yahan tak ke ham ne tamanna ki ke unhon-ne aap se ye sawal na kya hota, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kaho : aey Allah ! rehmat farma Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aal par, jaisey tu ney rehmat farmai Ibrahim ki aal par aur barkat nazil farma Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aal par, jaisey tu ney sab jahaanon mein barkat nazil farmai Ibrahim ki aal par, bila shubah to sazaware-hamd hai, azmaton wala hai aur salam isi tarah hai jaisey tum (pahley) jaan chukey ho."
908,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine ibne-abi-Lela se suna, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) miley aur kehney lagey : kya main tumhen aik tohfa na dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari taraf tashrif laey to ham ne kaha : ham to jaan chukey hain ke ham aap par salam kaise bhejein , (ye bataein ( ham aap par Salat (Durud) kaise bhejein ? aap ne farmaya : kaho : aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aal par rehmat farma, jaisey tu ney Ibrahim ki aal par rehmat farmai, bila shubah to sazawar hamd , azmaton wala hai. aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aal par barkat nazil farma, jaisey tu ney Ibrahim ki aal par barkat nazil farmai, bila shubah to sazaware-hamd hai, azmaton wala hai."
909,Wakee ne Shoba aur Misar se isi sanad ke sath hukm se usi ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki aur Misar ki hadis mein ye jumla nahi hai : kya main tumhen aik tohfa na dun?
910,"Ismail bin Zakariya ne Aamash , Misar aur Maalik-bin-Mighwal se riwayat ki aur un sab ne hukm se isi sanad ke sath pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki, albatta Ismail ne kaha : ( w baarak ala Muhammad (aur (is se pahley) ( اللهم ( nahi kaha,"
911,"Amr bin Sulaim ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat abu Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke unhon ( sahaba ( ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ham aap par Salat (Durud) kaise bhejein ? aap ne farmaya : kaho : aey Allah ! rehmat farma Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aur aap ki beeviyon aur aap ki aulad par, jaisey tu ney Ibrahim ki aal par rehmat farmai aur barkat nazil farma Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aur aap ki beeviyon aur aap ki aulad par, jaisey tu ney barkat nazil farmai Ibrahim ki aal par, bila shubah to sazaware-hamd hai, azmaton wala hai."
912,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne mujh par aik baar durood bheja Allah Taala is par das baar rehmat nazil farmaeyga .
913,"Sumai ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab imam ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( ) Allah ne sun liya jisne uski tareef ki) kahey to tum kaho : ( اللهم , ربنا لك الحمد ( ) aey Allah ! hamarey rab! sab tareef terey liye hai) kyonke jiska qaul farishton ke qaul ke muwafiq ho gaya iske guzishta gunah maaf kar diye jaengey."
914,"Suhel ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (uper zikr ki gaee rawi ( Sumai ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
915,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke un donon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab imam Aameen kahey to tum bhi Aameen kaho kyonke jiski Aameen farishton ki Aameen ke muwafiq ho jaeygi, iske pichhli gunah maaf kar diye jaengey. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aameen kehtey they."
916,"( Malik ke bajaey) Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. . .) aagey ( Malik ki uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ki tarah hai, albatta Yunus ne ibne-Shahab ka qaul bayan nahi kya."
917,abu Yunus ( Saleem bin Juber ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein Aameen kahey aur Farishtey aasman mein Aameen kahin aur aik Aameen dusri ke muwafiq ho jaey to iske pichhley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
918,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik aur shagird Aaraj ke hawale se riwayat hai ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se aik shakhs Aameen kahey aur Farishtey aasman mein Aameen kahin aur Aameen dusri ke muwafiq ho jaey to us shakhs ke pichhley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
919,Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ( guzishta hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
920,Suhel ke walid Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab qaari (غير المغضوب عليهم wla الضالين) kahey aur jo iske peechhey hai wo ( bhi) Aameen kahey aur iska kehna aasman walon ki kahi hui ( Aameen (ke muwafiq ho jaey to iske pichhley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
921,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey se gir gaey to aap ka dayan pahlu chhal gaya, ham aap ke yahan aap ki iyaadat ke liye hazir huey, Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to aap ne hamein baith kar Namaz padhai , chunanche ham ne (aap ke ishaarey par, hadis 926 . 928 (aap ke peechhey baith kar Namaz padhi, phir jab aap ne Namaz poori ki to farmaya : imam usi liye banaya gaya ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey, chunanche jab wo takbeer kahey to tum takbeer kaho , jab wo sajda karey to tum sajda karo, jab wo ( sar ( uthaey to tum ( sar ( uthao aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( ) Allah ne usey sun liya jisne uski hamd bayan ki) kahey to tum ( ربنا لك الحمد ( ) aey hamarey rab! terey hi liye sab tareef hai) kaho aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar Namaz padho."
922,"( Sufiyan ke bajaey) Leis ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey se gir gaey aur aap ka aik pahlu chhil gaya to aap ne hamein baith kar Namaz padhai. . . . aagey pichhli hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
923,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey se gir gaey aur aap ka dayan pahlu chhal gaya. . . phir un donon hazraat ( Sufiyan aur Leis ( ki riwayat ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta Yunus ne ye izafa kya : aur jab wo (imaam) khada ho kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar Namaz padho"
924,"Malik-bin-Anas ne Zohri se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey par Sawar huey aur us se gir padey , us se aap ka dayan pahlu chhil gaya. . . . aagey uper zikr ki gaee teenon rawiyon ki tarah riwayat ki aur us main ( bhi ye ( hai : jab wo (imam) khada ho kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar Namaz padho."
925,"Mamar ne Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey se gir padey jis se aap ka dayan pahlu chhil gaya. . . aagey pichhli hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, usmein Yunus aur Malik wala izafa nahi hai."
926,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham (bin Urwa ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar ho gaey, aap ke sahaba mein se kuchh log aap ke paas aap ki beemar pursi ke liye hazir huey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baith kar Namaz padhi to unhon-ne aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein khadey ho kar Namaz padhni shuru ki. aap ne unhein ishara kya ke baith jao to wo baith gaey. jab aap Namaz se farigh ho gaey to aap ne farmaya : imam isi liye banaya jata hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey, jab wo rukoo karey to tum rukoo karo aur jab wo ( rukoo w sujood se sar) uthaey to ( phir ( tum ( bhi sar ( uthao aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar Namaz padho."
927,Hammad-bin-Zaid aur Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki.
928,Leis ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari main ham ne aap ke peechhey is tarah Namaz padhi ke aap ne baith kar Namaz padhai aur hazarat siddeeq akbar (Raziallahu anhu) mukabbir ki haisiyat main takbirat kehtey they ‌ . Namaz main hamein khada dekh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein baithney ka hukm diya to ham baith gaey phir baad faraghat Namaz irshad hua tum ne us waqt wo kaam kya jaisa ke Faras aur Rome (mojooda Itly) waley apne badshah ke samney khadey rahtey hain aur badshah betha rehta hai ‌ . ‌ab aainda aisa na karna balke hameshaa apne imam ki pairvi karo agar wo baith kar Namaz padhaaey to tum bhi baith kar Namaz padho ‌ .
929,Abdur-Rehman Ruwasi ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Namaz padhai aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechhey they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) takbeer kehtey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi takbeer kehtey taake hamein sunaein . . . . phir Leis ki uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ki tarah bayan kya.
930,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : imam iqtida (pairvi) hi ke liye banaya gaya hai, isliye uski mukhalifat na karo, chunanche jab wo takbeer kahey to tum takbeer kaho aur jab wo rukoo karey to tum rukoo karo aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to (tum اللهم , ربنا لك الحمد ( kaho aur jab wo sajda karey to tum sajda karo aur jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar Namaz padho."
931,Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat bayan ki.
932,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein taleem detey they, farmatey they : imam se aagey na badho , jab wo takbeer kahey to tum takbeer kaho , jab wo ( wla الضالين ( kahey to tum Aameen kaho aur jab wo rukoo karey to tum rukoo karo aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( اللهم , ربنا لك الحمد ( kaho."
933,"Suhel bin abi Saleh ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi (pichhli hadis) ke ham mana riwayat ki, siwaey us hissey ke : jab wo ( wla الضالين ( kahey to tum Aameen kaho , aur ye hissey badhaya : aur tum us se pahley ( sar ( na uthao."
934,"abu-Alqama ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yaqinan imam aik dhaal hai (tum iske peechhey peechhey raho ( , chunanche jab wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar Namaz padho aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( اللهم , ربنا لك الحمد ( kaho kyonke jab zamin waley ka kaha hua aasman walon ke kehney ke muwafiq ho jaeyga to iske pichhli gunah bakhsh diye jaengey."
935,"( abu-Alqama ke bajaey) Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Yunus ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : imam isliye banaya gaya hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey, jab wo takbeer kahey to tum takbeer kaho aur jab wo rukoo karey to tum rukoo karo aur jab wo ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kahey to tum ( اللهم ربنا لك الحمد ( kaho , aur jab wo khada ho kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi khadey ho kar padho aur jab wo baith kar padhey to tum bhi sab ke sab baith kar Namaz padho ."
936,"Musa bin abi Aaisha ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unse kaha : kya aap mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari ke barey mein nahi bataeingi ? unhon-ne kaha : kyon nahi ! jab ( bimari ke sabab ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke harkaat w saknaat ( bojhal honey lagey to aap ne farmaya : kya logon ne Namaz padh li ? ham ne kaha : Allah ke rasool! nahi, wo sab aap ka intizar kar rahe hain. aap ne farmaya : mere liye badey tasht mein pani rakho . ham ne pani rakha to aap ne ghusl farmaya : phir aap ne uthney ki koshish ki to aap par be-hoshi taari ho gaee, phir aapko fayda hua to farmaya : kya logon ne Namaz padhi li ? ham ne kaha : nahi, Allah ke rasool! wo aap ke muntazir hain. aap ne farmaya : mere liye badey tasht mein pani rakho . ham ne rakha to aap ne ghusl farmaya : phir aap uthney lagey to aap par ghashii taarii ho gaee, phir hosh mein aaey to farmaya : kya logon ne Namaz padh li hai? ham ne kaha : nahi, Allah ke rasool! wo aap ka intizar kar rahe hain. aap ne farmaya : mere liye badey tasht mein pani rakho . ham ne rakha to aap ne ghusl farmaya : phir uthney lagey to be-hosh ho gaey, phir hosh mein aaey to farmaya : kya logon ne Namaz padh li? ham ne kaha : nahi, Allah ke rasool! wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intizar kar hai hain. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : log masjid mein ikatthey baithey huey isha ki Namaz ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intizar kar rahe they. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf paigham bheja ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein. paigham laney wala unke paas aaya aur bola : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aapko hukm de rahe hain ke aap logon ko Namaz padhaaein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, aur wo bahut narm dil insan they : umr ! aap logon ko Namaz padhaaein. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap hi iske zyada haqdaar hain. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : un dinon Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon ko Namaz padhai , phir ye hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh kami mehsus farmai to 2 mardon ka sahara lekar , jin mein se aik Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) they, namaze-Zohar ke liye nikley, (is waqt) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko Namaz padha rahe they, jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko dekha to peechhey hatney lagey, is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ishara kya ke peechhey na hatein aur aap ne un donon se farmaya : mujhey unke pahlu mein bitha do. un donon ne aapko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke pahlu mein bitha diya, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padh rahe they aur log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki Namaz ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahe they aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat karne waley rawi ( Ubaidullah ne kaha : phir main Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur unse kaha : kya main aap ke samney wo hadis pesh na karun jo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari ke barey mein bayan ki hai? unhon-ne kaha : laao. to maine unke samney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki hadis pesh ki, unhon-ne usmein se kisi baat ka inkar na kya, haan ! itna kaha : kya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne tumhen us aadmi ka naam bataya jo Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath they? maine kaha : nahi. unhon-ne kaha : wo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they."
937,"Mamar ne bayan kya ke Zohri ne kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne khabar di ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne usey khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari ka shuruat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar se hua, aap ne apni beeviyon se ijazat mangi ke aap ki timar daari mere ghar mein ki jaey, unhon-ne ijazat de di. ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya : aap is tarah nikley ke aap ka aik hath Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) (ke kandhey ( par aur doosra hath aik doosrey aadmi par tha aur) naqahat ki wjah se) aap apne paon se zamin par lakeer banatey ja rahe they. Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke maine ye hadis Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum jantey ho wo aadmi , jiska Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne naam nahi liya, kon they? wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they."
938,"Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne kaha : ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( ne kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaee aur aap ki takleef mein izafa ho gaya to aap ne apni beeviyon se ijazat talab ki ke unki timar daari mere ghar mein ho, unhon-ne ijazat de di, phir aap 2 aadmiyon ke darmyan ( unka sahara lekar ( nikley, aap ke donon paon zamin par lakeer banatey ja rahe they (aur aap ( Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) aur aik doosrey aadmi ke darmyan they. ( hadis ke rawi ( Ubaidullah ne kaha : Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne jo kuchh kaha tha, maine iska tazkira Abdullah (bin Abbas ( (Raziallahu anhu) se kya to unhon-ne mujh se kaha : kya tum jantey ho wo aadmi kon tha jiska Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne naam nahi liya ? unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : nahi. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : wo Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) they."
939,"Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Utba-bin- Masood ne khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke maine (Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko imam banaaney ke) us mamley main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baar-baar baat ki. maine itni baar aap se sirf isliye rujoo kya ke mere dil mein ye baat baithti na thi ke log aap ke baad kabhi us shakhs se mohabbat karengey jo aap ka qaaim maqam hoga aur uske bar-aks mera khayal ye tha ke aap ki jagah par jo shakhs bhi khada hoga log usey bura ( burey shagoon ka haamil) samjhengey, isliye main chahti thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) imamat (ki zimme-dari ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se hata dein."
940,"(Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah ke bajaey) Hamza bin-Abdullah-bin umr ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( bimari ke doran mein) mere ghar tashrif ley aaey to aap ne farmaya : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm pahunchaao ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein. wo kehti hain : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) narm dil insan hain, jab wo Quran padhengey to apne aansuon par qaabu nahi rakh sakengey , lihaza agar aap Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke bajaey kisi aur ko hukm dein (to behtar hoga.) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : Allah ki qism ! mere dil mein us cheez ko na-pasand karne ki iske ilawa aur koi baat na thi ke jo shakhs sabse pahley aap ki jagah khada hoga log usey bura samjhein gey , isliye maine 2 ya teen baar apni baat dohrai to aap ne farmaya : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hi logon ko Namaz padhaaein , bila shubah tum Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke sath ( mamla karne) wali auratein hi ho."
941,"abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaee to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aapko Namaz ki itlaa dene ke liye hazir huey. aap ne farmaya : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaho wo Namaz padhaaein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jald gham zada ho janey waley insan hain aur wo jab aap ki jagah khadey hongey to logon ko) qirat bhi) nahi suna sakengey , lihaza agar aap umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm de dein (to behtar hoga.) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( phir ( farmaya : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaho ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein. , maine Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : tum Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaho ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jald ghamzada hone-wale insan hain, jab wo aap ki jagah par khadey hongey to logon ko) qirat ( na suna sakengey , chunanche agar aap umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm dein (to behtar hoga.) Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne aap se keh diya to aap ne farmaya : tum Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke sath ( mamla karne) wali aurton hi ki tarah ho, Abu-Bakar se kaho ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : logon ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm pahuncha diya to unhon-ne logon ko Namaz padhai. jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz shuru kar di to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tabeeat mein qadrey kami mehsus ki, aap uthey , 2 aadmi aapko sahara diye huey they aur aap ke paon zamin par lakeer kheenchtey ja rahe they. wo farmati hain : jab aap masjid mein dakhil huey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ki aahat sun li, wo peechhey hatney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ishara kya ke apni jagah khadey raho, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badhey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baain taraf baith gaey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith kar logon ko Namaz padha rahe they aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahe they aur log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) kar rahe they."
942,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki. un donon ki hadis mein hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us marz mein mubtala huey jis mein aap ne wafat paai . ibne-Mus-hir ki riwayat mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko laya gaya yahan tak ke unhein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke pahlu mein bitha diya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ko Namaz padha rahe they aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko takbeer suna rahe they. Esa ki riwayat mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith gaey aur logon ko Namaz padhaaney lagey, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke pahlu mein they aur logon ko (aap ki takbeer ( suna rahe they."
943,"aik aur sanad ke sath Hisham ne apne walid (Urwa) se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni bimari mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein to wo unko Namaz padhatey rahe. Urwa ne kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni tabeeat mein kuchh halkapan mehsus kya, to aap bahar tashrif laaey, us waqt Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ki imamat kar rahe they. jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko dekha to peechhey hatney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ishara kya ke jaisey ho waisey hi raho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke barabar unke pahlu mein baith gaey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki imamat mein Namaz ada kar rahe they aur log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padh rahe they."
944,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari ke doran , jis mein aap ne wafat paai , Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko Namaz padhatey they yahan tak ke jab peer ka din aaya aur sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz mein saf basta they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hujrey ka parda uthaya aur hamari taraf dekha, us waqt aap khadey huey they, aisa lagta tha ke aap ka rukh anwar musahaf ka aik waraq hai, phir aap ne hanstey huey tabassum farmaya, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ham Namaz hi mein us khushi ke sabab jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bahar aaney se hui thi mabhoot ho kar reh gaey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ultey paon lautey taake saf mein mil jayen, unhon-ne samjha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye bahar tashrif la rahe hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se ishara farmaya ke apni Namaz mukammal karo, phir aap wapas hujrey mein dakhil ho gaey aur parda latkaa diya. isi din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wafat pa gaey."
945,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne (ibne-Shahab) Zohri se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf maine jo aakhiri nazar dali (wo is tarah thi ke) peer ke din aap ne ( hujrey ka ( parda uthaya . . . . jis tarah uper waqia ( bayan hua) hai. (Imam Muslim farmatey hain : ( Saleh ki hadis kaamil aur sair hasil hai."
946,"Mamar ne Zohri ke hawale se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke jab peer ka din aaya. . . . uper waley donon rawiyon ke mutabiq ."
947,"Abdul-Azeez ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( bimari ke dinon mein) teen din hamari taraf tashrif na laaey, ( unhi dinon mein se) aik din Namaz khadi ki gaee aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aagey badhney lagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kamrey ke) pardey ki taraf badhey aur usey utha diya, jab hamarey samney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka rukh anwar khula to ham ne kabhi aisa manzar na dekha tha jo hamarey liye, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak ke nazaarey se, jo hamarey samney tha, zyada Husain aur pasandida ho. wo kehtey hain : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko hath se ishara kya ke wo aagey badhin aur aap ne parda gira diya, phir aap wafat tak aisa na kar sakey."
948,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar ho gaey aur aap ki bimari ne shiddat ikhtiyar ki to aap ne farmaya : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaho ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : wo narm dil aadmi hain, jab aap ki jagah khadey hongey to logon ko Namaz na padha sakengey . aap ne farmaya : (aey Aaisha ! ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaho ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein , tum to Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke sath ( mamla karne) waaliyon ki tarah ho. unhon ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : is tarah Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein logon ko Namaz padhaaney lagey."
949,"Imam Malik ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) banu-Amr bin Auf ke yahan , unke darmyan suleh karaaney ke liye tashrif ley gaey. us doran mein Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to muazzan Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kaha : kya aap logon ko Namaz padhaaeingey taake main takbeer kahun ? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : haan. unhon ( Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : is tarah Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz shuru kar di, itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey jabke log Namaz mein they, aap bach kar guzartey huey ( pehli ( saf mein pahunch kar khadey ho gaey. is par logon ne hathon ko hathon par mar kar awaz karni shuru kar di Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apni Namaz mein kisi aur taraf tawajjoh nahi detey they. jab logon ne musalsal hathon se awaz ki to wo mutwajjeh huey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ishara kya ke apni jagah khadey rahen , is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne donon hath uthaey aur Allah ka shukr ada kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko is baat ka hukm diya, phir iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) peechhey hat kar saf mein sahi tarah khadey ho gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badhey aur aap ne Namaz padhai. jab aap farigh huey to farmaya : aey Abu-Bakar ! jab maine tumhen hukm diya to apni jagah tikey rehney se tumhen kis cheez ne rok diya ? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : abu-Qahafa ke betey ke liye zebaa na tha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey ( khadey ho kar) jamat kiraaey , phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar) farmaya : kya hua? maine tum logon ko dekha ke tum bahut taaliyan bajaa rahe they? jab Namaz main tumhen koi aisi baat pesh aa jaey (jis par tawajjoh dilaana zaroori ho ( to Subhan-Allah kaho , jab koi Subhan-Allah kahega to uski taraf tawajjoh ki jaeygi, hath par hath maarna, sirf aurton ke liye hai."
950,"Abdul-Azeez bin abi Hazim aur Yaqoob bin Abdur-Rehman al-Qadri donon ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se Imam Malik ki riwayat ki tarah riwayat bayan ki. un donon ki hadis mein ye hai ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne donon hath buland kiye, Allah Taala ka shukriya ada kya aur ultey paon wapas huey yahan tak ke saf mein aa khadey huey."
951,"Ubaidullah ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabila banu-Amr-bin-Auf ke darmyan suleh karaaney tashrif ley gaey. . . . aagey uper zikr ki gaee rawiyon ki tarah ( hadis bayan ki) aur is mein ye izafa kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aaey aur safon ko cheertey huey pehli saf ke qareeb khadey ho gaey. usmein ye alfaz bhi hain ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ultey paon peechhey lot aaey."
952,"Ibad bin Ziyad ko Urwa-bin-Mugheera-bin-Shoba ne khabar di ke Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ghaz wo Tabook mein Sharik huey. Mughira ne kaha : subah ki Namaz se pahley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye bahar nikley aur maine aap ke sath pani ka aik bartan utha liya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri taraf lautey to main bartan se aap ke hathon par pani dalney laga, aap ne apne donon hath teen baar dhoey , phir apna chehra dhoya , iske baad apne donon hathon se jubba nikalney lagey, jubbey ki donon aasteenein tang huin to aap ne apne hath jubbey ke andar kar liye yahan tak ke aap ne apne bazu jubbey ke nichey se nikal liye aur donon hath kohniyon tak dhoey , phir apne donon mozon par masah ( karke ( wuzu ( mukammal ( kya, phir aap aagey badhey . Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main bhi aap ke sath aagey badha yahan tak ke ham ne logon ko us haal mein paya ke wo Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko aagey kar chukey they, unhon-ne Namaz padhai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko 2 rakaton mein se aik mili . aap ne aakhiri rakaat logon ke sath ada ki, chunanche jab Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne salam phera to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni Namaz ki takmeel ke liye khadey ho gaey, is baat ne musalmanon ko ghabraahat mein mubtala kar diya aur unhon-ne kasarat se Subhan-Allah kehna shuru kar diya, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni Namaz poori kar li to unki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya : tum ne achchha kya. ya farmaya : tum ne theek kya. aap ne unki tahseen farmai ke unhon-ne waqt par Namaz padh li thi."
953,Ismail bin Muhammad-bin Sad ne Hamza bin Mughira se riwayat ki jo Ibad ki riwayat ki tarah hai. (is mein ye bhi hai ke) Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko peechhey karna chaha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey ( aagey ( rehney do.
954,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Amr Naqid aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, neez Harun bin Maruf aur Hurmala bin Yahya ne kaha : hamein ibne- Wahab ne bataya , unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Yunus ne ibne-Shahab ke hawale se khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (Imam ko mutanabbeh karne ka tariqa ( mardon ke liye tasbeeh (Subhan-Allah kehna) hai aur aurton ke liye hath par hath maarna hai. Hurmala ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya ke ibne-Shahab ne kaha : maine ilm waley logon ko dekha, wo tasbeeh kehtey they aur ishara kartey they."
955,Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi (pichhli riwayat ( ki tarah riwayat bayan ki hai.
956,Hammam ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ( uper zikr ki gaee hadis) ki tarah riwayat bayan ki aur is mein izafa kya : Namaz main ( mutanabbeh karne ke liye. (
957,"Saeed ke walid abu-Saeed Maqbari ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( hamein ( Namaz padhai , phir salam phera aur farmaya : aey falan ! tum apni Namaz achi tarah nahi padh saktey ? kya namazi Namaz padhtey waqt ye nahi dekhta ( ghaur karta (ke wo Namaz kaisey padhta hai? wo apne hi liye Namaz padhta hai) kisi doosrey ke liye nahi. ( Allah ki qism ! main apne peechhey bhi isi tarah dekhta hun jis tarah samney dekhta hun"
958,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum samajhtey ho ke mera rukh idhar ( samney ( hi hai? Allah ki qism ! mujh par na tumhara rukoo makhfi hai aur na tumhara sajda , yaqinan main tumhen apne peechhey bhi dekhta hun."
959,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : rukoo aur sajda poori tarah kya karo, Allah ki qism ! main tumhen apne peechhey ( bhi) dekhta hun. ( balke) ghaaliban aap ne is tarah farmaya : jab tum rukoo aur sajda kartey ho to main tumhen apni peeth peechhey bhi dekhta hun."
960,"Qatada se (Shoba ke bajaey dustwai waale) Hisham aur Saeed ne apni apni sanad ke sath Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : rukoo aur sajda ko mukammal karo, Allah ki qism ! jab bhi tum rukoo kartey ho aur jab bhi tum sajda kartey ho to main apni peeth peechhey tumhen dekhta hun aur Saeed ki riwayat main ( إذا ما ركعتم وإذا ما سجدتم (ke bajaey) ( إذا ركعتم وسجدتم ( jab tum rukoo aur sajda kartey ho. ke alfaz hain. yani Saeed ki riwayat main ( اذا (ke baad donon jagah ( ما (ka lafz nahi hai."
961,"Mina saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din Namaz padhaaney ke fauran hi baad hamari taraf mutwajjeh ho kar farmaya : '' logo ! main tumhara imam hun. isliye mujh se pahley rukoo , sajda , qauma aur salam na phero . main aagey aur peechhey se tum ko dekhta hun aur qism hai us zaat ki jiske qabze mein meri jaan hai jo cheezein mein dekhta hun agar tum unhein dekh lo to hanso kam aur roo zyada. logon ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne kya dekha hai? irshad hua ''maine jannat aur dozakh dekhi hai.''"
962,"(Ali-bin-Mus-hir ke bajaey) Jarir aur ibne-Fuzail donon ne apni apni sanad se Mukhtar-bin-Fulful se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki, Jarir ki hadis mein na salam pherney mein ke alfaz nahi."
963,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs imam se pahley (rukoo w sujood se) sar uthata hai kya wo is baat se nahi darta ke Allah Taala uske sar ko gadhey ke sar jaisa bana de?"
964,Yunus ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs apni Namaz mein imam se pahley sar uthata hai wo is baat se mehfooz nahi ke Allah Taala uski sura gadhey ki sura mein badal de.
965,"Rabe-bin-Muslim, Shoba aur Hammaad-bin-Salma sab ne mukhtalif sanadon se Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne yahi riwayat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki. (un rawiyon mein se) Rabe-bin-Muslim ki hadis main ( uski sura badal de ke bajaey) aur Allah iska chehra gadhey ka chehra bana de ke alfaz hain."
966,Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo log Namaz main apni nazrein aasman ki taraf uthatey hain wo har sura (apni us harkat se) baaz aa jayen warna (ho sakta hai unki nazar ( unki taraf na lautey ( salb kar li jaey. (
967,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : log Namaz mein dua ke waqt apni nazrein aasman ki taraf buland karne se laziman baaz aa jayen ya ( phir aisa ho sakta hai ke) unki nazrein uchak li jaaein.
968,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Musaiyab bin Raafe se, unhon-ne Tameem bin tarfa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nikal kar hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya : kya wjah hai ke main tumhen Namaz mein is tarah hath uthatey dekh raha hun, jaisey wo bidaktey huey sarkash ghodon ki dumein hon ? ( hath utha kar daain baain ghodey ki dam ki tarah kyon hilatey ho. dekhiye , hadis : 970 . 971 ( Namaz mein pur-sukoon raho. unhon-ne kaha : phir aap (eik aur mauqe par) tashrif laey aur hamein mukhtalif halqon mein baithey dekha to farmaya : kya wjah hai ke tumhen toliyon main ( bata hua) dekh raha hoon? phir (eik aur mauqe par) tashrif laey to farmaya : tum is tarah saf bandi kyon nahi kartey jis tarah bargahe-Ilahi mein Farishtey saf basta hotey hain? ham ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! Farishtey Allah Taala ki bargah mein kis tarah saf bandi kartey hain? aap ne farmaya : wo pehli safon ko mukammal kartey hain aur saf mein aik doosrey ke sath jad kar khadey hotey hain."
969,Wakee aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne (apni apni sanad se riwayat kartey huey) kaha : hamein Aamash ne isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee hadis bayan ki.
970,"Misar ne kaha : mujh se Ubaidullah ibne- qibtiya ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha ke jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey to ham kehtey : ( Assalamualaikum ورحمة الله , Assalamualaikum ورحمة الله (aur unhon-ne apne hath se donon taraf ishara kya, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apne hathon ke sath ishara kyon kartey ho, jaisey wo bidaktey huey sarkash ghodon ki dumein hon ? tum mein se (har ( aik ke liye bas yahi kafi hai ke apne hath apni raan par rakhey , phir apne bhai ko salam karey jo daain taraf hai aur (jo ( baain taraf ( hai.) ,"
971,"Furaat Qazzaz ne Ubaidullah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi ham log jab salam phertey to hathon ke ishaarey se ( Assalamualaikum , Assalamualaikum ( kehtey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari taraf dekha aur farmaya : kya wjah hai ke tum hathon se is tarah ishara kartey ho, jaisey wo bidaktey huey sarkash ghodon ki dumen hon? tum mein se koi jab salam pherey to apne sathi ki taraf rukh karey aur hath se ishara na kare."
972,"Abdullah-bin-Idris , abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne Aamash se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Umara bin Umer Taimi se, unhon-ne abu Mamar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz main ( hamein barabar khada karne ke liye) hamarey kandhon ko hath laga kar farmatey : barabar ho jao aur juda judaa khadey na ho ke us se tumharey dil aapas mein mukhtalif ho jayen, mere sath tum mein se pukhta aql waley daanishmand ( khadey ( hon, unke baad wo jo (daanish mandi mein) unke qareeb hon, phir wo jo unke qareeb hun. abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aaj tum aik doosrey se shadeed tareen ikhtilaf rakhtey ho."
973,"Jareer, Esa-bin-Yonus aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne (Aamash se) baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki."
974,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere sath tum mein se pukhta aql waley aur daanish mand khadey hon, phir wo jo (is mein) unke qareeb hon ( phir wo jo unke qareeb hon, phir wo jo unke qareeb hon ( teen baar farmaya : aur tum bazaron ke gadmad giroh ( banney ( se bacho."
975,"Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apni safon ko barabar kya karo kyonke safon ka barabar karna Namaz ki takmeel ka hissa hai."
976,"Abdul-Azeez ne, jo Suheb ke betey hain, Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : safain poori karo, main apni peeth peechhey tumhen dekhta hun."
977,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hai jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kya, phir unhon-ne unmein se bahut si hadisein bayan kiin aur kaha : Namaz mein saf seedhi rakho kyonke saf ko seedha rakhna Namaz ke Hasan ( adaaeygi (ka hissa hai."
978,"Saalim-bin abi Jaad ghatfaani ne kaha : maine Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : tum har sura apni safon ko barabar rakho warna Allah Taala laziman tumharey rukh aik doosrey ki mukhalif samton mein kar dega."
979,"abu khaisma ne Samak-bin-Harab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari safon ko (is qadr ( seedha aur barabar karatey they, maano aap unke zariey se teeron ko seedha kar rahe hain, yahan tak ke jab aapko yaqin ho gaya ke ham ne aap se (is baat ko) achi tarah samajh liya hai to iske baad aik din aap ghar se nikal kar tashrif laey aur (namaz padhaaney ki jagah ( khadey ho gaey aur qareeb tha ke aap takbeer kahin (aur Namaz shuru farma dein ke) aap ne aik aadmi ko dekha, iska Sina saf se kuchh aagey nikla hua tha, aap ne farmaya : Allah ke bando! tum lazimi taur par apni safon ko seedha karo warna Allah tumharey rukh aik doosrey ke khilaf mod dega."
980,abu-Ahwas aur abu-Awana ne apni apni sanad ke sath ( Samak se) uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki.
981,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar log jaan lein ke azan ( kehney (aur pehli saf (ka hissey banney ( mein kya ( khair w barkat ( hai, phir wo uski khaatir Qura andazi karne ke siwa koi chaara na paaein to wo uske liye Qura andazi ( bhi) karein aur agar wo jaan lein ke Zohar (ki Namaz ( jaldi ada karne mein kitna ajr w sawab milta hai to uske liye aik doosrey se sabqat ley janey ki koshish karengey aur agar unhein malum ho jaey ke isha aur subah ki namazon mein kitna sawab hai to un donon namazon main (har sura ( pahunchein chahey ghisat ghisat kar aana padey ."
982,"abu-Ash-hab ne abu-Nazara abdi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon ko) saf bandi mein) peechhey rahtey dekha to unse kaha : aagey badho aur) seedhey-seedhey ( meri iqtida (pairvi) karo aur jo log tumharey baad hon wo tumhari iqtida (pairvi) karein, kuchh log musalsal peechhey rahtey jaeinge yahan tak ke Allah Taala unko peechhey kar dega."
983,"Jurairi ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko masjid ke pichhley hissey mein dekha. . . aagey isi tarah riwayat bayan ki."
984,"Ibrahim bin-Dinar aur Muhammad-bin Harab Wasti ne kaha : hamein abu-Qatan Amr bin Haisam ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Qatada se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Khilas se, unhon-ne abu Raafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum jaan lo, ya log jaan lein ke agli saf mein kya ( fazeelat ( hai to is par Qura andazi ho. ibne- Harab ne ( في الصف المقدم لكانت قرعة (ke bajaey) ( في الصف الأول ما كانت إلا قرعة ( pehli saf mein kya hai to Qura ke siwa kuchh na ho kaha,"
985,Jarir ne Suhel se unhon-ne apne walid se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mardon ki behtreen saf pehli aur badtareen saf aakhiri hai jabke aurton ki behtreen saf aakhiri aur badtareen saf pehli hai.
986,"Abdul-Azeez , yani darawardi ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( riwayat bayan ki hai."
987,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine mardon ko dekha ke chaadrein tang honey ki wjah se wo bachchon ki tarah apni chaadrein gardanon mein baandhey huey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padh rahe they, is par kisi kehney waley ne kaha : aey aurton ki jamat ! tum us waqt tak apne saron ko) sajdey se) na uthana jab tak mard ( sar na ( utha lein. ( khuda-n-khasta kisi mard ke sattar ka koi hissey khula hua na ho. ye baat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mojudgi mein kahi gaee aur aap ne kehney waley ko na toka.)"
988,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Salim se suna, wo apne walid se riwayat bayan kar rahe they aur wo ( iski sanad mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchtey they (ke (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi se uski biwi masjid janey ki ijazat maangey to wo usey na rokey ."
989,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Salim bin-Abdullah ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : apni aurton ko jab wo tum se masjidon mein janey ki ijazat talab karein to unhein ( wahan janey se) na roko .) Salim ne) kaha : to ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke doosrey betey ( Bilal bin-Abdullah ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham to unko zaroor rokengey. is par hazarat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski taraf rukh kya aur usko sakht bura bhala kaha, maine unhein kabhi ( kisi ko) itna bura bhala kehtey nahi suna aur kaha : main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman bata raha hun aur tum kehtey ho : Allah ki qism ! ham unhein zaroor rokengey."
990,Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki baandiyon ko Allah ki masaajid se na roko .
991,"Hanzala ne kaha : maine Salim se suna, keh rahe they : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jab tumhari auratein tum se masaajid mein janey ki ijazat maangein to unhein ijazat de do."
992,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Mujahid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : raat ko aurton ko masjidon mein janey se na roko . to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik betey ne kaha : ham unko nahi chhodengey ke wo jayen aur usey kharabi aur bigaad (ka zariey ( bana lein. ( Mujahid ne) kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey sakht daanta aur kaha : main kehta hun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur to kehta hai ham unhein nahi chhodengey ."
993,doosrey shagird Esa ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah khabar di
994,"(Aamash ke bajaey) Amr (bin Dinar Johmi) ne Mujahid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aurton ko raat ke waqt masjidon ki taraf nikalney ki ijazat do. to unke betey ne, jis ko Waqid kaha jata tha, kaha : tab wo usko kharabi w bigaad bana lengi. ( Mujahid ne) kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske seeney par maara aur kaha : ! main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis suna raha hun aur to kehta hai : nahi !"
995,"( khud ( Bilal bin-Abdullah-bin umr ne apne walid Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aurton ko jab wo tum se ijazat talab karein to masjidon mein jo unke hissey hain un (ke husool ( se (unhein ( na roko . Bilal ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham unko zaroor rokengey . Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : main keh raha hun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur to kehta hai : ham unhein zaroor rokengey"
996,"Makhrima ne apne walid ( Bukair ( se, unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Zenab Saqfiya (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (ye ( hadis bayan karti thin, aap ne farmaya : jab tum aurton mein se koi isha ki Namaz mein shamil ho to wo us raat khushbu na lagaey ."
997,"( Makhrima ke bajaey) Muhammad-bin Ajlan ne Bukair bin-Abdullah-bin ashajj se unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood ( (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein hukm diya tha : jab tum mein se koi masjid mein jaey to wo khushbu ko hath na lagaey"
998,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis aurat ko (bakhor) khushbudar dhuan lag jaey wo hamarey sath isha ki Namaz mein hazir na ho."
999,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se aur unhon-ne Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, wo farmati thin ke aurton ne ( banao singar ke) jo naey andaz nikal liye hain agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekh letey to unhein masjid mein aaney se rok detey, jis tarah Bani-Israil ki aurton ko rok diya gaya tha. maine Umra se puchha : kya Bani-Israil ki aurton ko masjid mein aaney se rok diya gaya tha? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
1000,"( Sulaiman-bin Bilal ke bajaey) Abdul Wahab Saqafi , Sufiyan-bin-Uena, abu-Khalid Ahmar aur Esa bin Yunus sabhii ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se ( baqi bachi ( isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis riwayat ki hai"
1001,"Saeed-bin-Jubair ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Allah Taala ke farman : ( wla تجهر بصلاتك wla تخافت بها (aur apni Namaz na buland awaz se padhein aur na usey past karein ke barey mein riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ye aayat us waqt utri jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein posheeda ( ibadat kartey ( they. jab aap apne sathiyon ko jamat karatey to qirat buland awaz se kartey they, mushrik jab ye qirat suntey to Quran ko , iske nazil karne waley ko aur uske laney waley ko bura bhala kehtey. is par Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hidayat ki : apni Namaz main ( awaz ko is qadr ( buland na karein ke aap ki qirat mushrikon ko sunai de aur na us (ki awaz ( ko past karein apne sathiyon se, unhein Quran sunain aur awaz itni ziyada unchi na karein aur un ( donon (ke darmyan ki raah ikhtiyar karein. ( Allah Taala ( farmata hai : buland aur aahista ke darmyan (main rahen. ("
1002,"Yahya bin Zakariya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Allah Taala ke usi farman : na apni Namaz main ( qirat ( buland karein aur na aahista , ke barey mein riwayat ki ke unhon-ne ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha ke ye aayat dua ke barey mein utri hai."
1003,"Hammad-bin-Zaid, abu-Usama, Wakee aur abu-Muawiya ne apni-apni sanad ke sath Hisham se usi pichhli sanad ke sath yahi hadis riwayat ki hai."
1004,"Jarir bin abdul-Hameed ne Musa bin abi Aaisha se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Allah Taala ke farman : (لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به (aap iske sath apni zaban ko harkat na dein taake usey jaldi hasil kar lein. ke barey mein riwayat bayan ki kaha : jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas wahi lekar aatey to aap ( usko padhney ke liye saath-saath ( apni zaban aur apne honton ko harkat detey they, aisa karna aap par nagawar guzarta tha aur ye aap (ke chehrey ( se malum ho jata. is par Allah Taala ne ye aayatein utaarin : aap us ( wahi ke padhney (ke liye apni zaban ko na hilaaein ke aap usey jald seekh lein. be-shak usko (aap ke dil mein) samet rakhna aur (aap ki zaban se) uski qirat hamara zimma hai. yani hamara zimma hai ke ham usey aap ke Sina Mubarak mein jama karein aur uski qirat ( bhi hamarey zimmey hai) taake aap qirat karein. phir jab ham usey padhein ( farishta hamari taraf se tilawat karey) to aap iske padhney ki ittaba (pairvi) karein. farmaya : yani ham usko nazil karein to aap usko ghaur se sunein . iska waazeh kar dena bhi yaqinan hamarey zimmey hai ke aap ki zaban se ( logon ke samney ( bayan kar dein, phir jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aap ke paas ( wahi lekar ( aatey to aap sar jhukaa kar ghaur se suntey aur jab wo chaley jatey to Allah ke waadey ke mutabiq aap uski qirat farmatey."
1005,"( Jarir bin abdul-Hameed ke bajaey) abu-Awana ne Musa bin abi Aaisha se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se Allah ke farman : aap us ( wahi ko padhney (ke liye apni zaban ko na hilaaein ke aap usey jald seekh lein, ke barey mein riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahi ke nuzool ki wjah se bahut mashaqqat bardasht kartey, aap ( saath-saath ( apne hont hilatey they (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey kaha : main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tarah hont hila kar dikhata hun, to unhon-ne apne honton ko harkat di aur Saeed-bin-Jubair ne (apne shagird se) kaha : main apne honton ko isi tarah hilata hun jis tarah Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) unhein hilatey they, phir apne hont hilaaey ( is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat utari : aap us ( wahi ko padhney (ke liye apni zaban ko na hilaaein ke aap usey jald seekh lein. be-shak hamara zimma hai usko (aap ke dil mein) samet kar rakhna aur (aap ki zaban se) uski qirat. kaha : aap ke seeney mein usey jama karna, phir ye ke aap usey padhein. phir jab ham padhein ( farishta hamari taraf se tilawat karey) to aap iske padhney ki ittaba (pairvi) karein. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : yani usko ghaur se sunein aur khamosh rahen , phir hamarey zimmey hai ke aap uski qirat karein. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : iske baad jab aap ke paas Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ( wahi lekar ( aatey to aap ghaur se suntey aur jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) chaley jatey to usey aap isi tarah padhtey jis tarah unhon-ne aapko padhaya hota."
1006,"Saeed-bin-Jubair ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jinon ko Quran sunaya na unko dekha. ( asl waqia ye hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne chand sathiyon ko sath Ukaaz ke bazar ki taraf janey ke iraadey se chaley (un dinon ( aasmani khabar aur shaitanon ke darmyan rukawat paida kar di gaee thi ( shaitan aasmani khabrein na sun saktey they) aur un par angaarey phainkey janey lagey they, to shayatin ( khabrein hasil kiye baghair ( apni qaum ke paas wapas aaey. is par unhon-ne puchha : tumharey sath kya hua? unhon ( wapas aaney walon ( ne kaha : hamein aasman ki khabrein leney se rok diya gaya aur ham par angaarey phainkey gaey. unhon-ne kaha : iske siwa ye kisi aur sabab se nahi hua ke koi nai baat zuhoor pazeer hui hai, isliye tum zamin ke mashriq w maghrib mein phail jao aur dekho ke hamarey aur aasmani khabar ke darmyan haail honey wali cheez (ki haqiqat ( kya hai? wo nikal kar zamin ke mashriq aur maghrib mein pahunchey . wo nafri jisne tahaama ka rukh kya tha, guzri , to aap Ukaaz ki taraf jatey huey kajhooron ( waley maqam nakhla ( mein they, apne sathiyon ko subah ki Namaz padha rahe they, jab jinon ne Quran suna to is par kaan laga diye aur kehney lagey : ye hai jo hamarey aur aasmanon ki khabar ke darmyan haail ho gaya hai. iske baad wo apni qaum ki taraf lautey aur kaha : aey hamari qaum ! ham ne ajeeb Quran suna hai jo haq ki taraf rehnumai karta hai, isliye ham is par eman ley aaey hain aur ham apne rab ke sath hargiz kisi ko Sharik nahi thehraengey. is par Allah Taala ne apne Nabi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye aayat nazil farmai : keh dijiye : meri taraf ye wahi ki gaee hai ke jinon ki aik jamat ne kaan laga kar suna."
1007,"Abdul-Aala ne Dawud se aur unhon-ne Aamir (bin Sharaheel) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Alqama se puchha : kya jinon (se mulaqat ( ki raat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah ke sath they? kaha : Alqama ne jawab diya : maine khud ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap logon mein se koi 'lailatul-Jin' mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maujood tha? unhon-ne kaha : nahi, lekin aik raat ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, to ham ne aapko gum paya , ham ne aapko wadiyon aur ghatiyon mein talash kya, (aap na miley ( to ham ne kaha ke aapko uda liya gaya hai ya aapko be khabri mein qatl kar diya gaya hai, kaha : ham ne badtareen raat guzari jo kisi qaum ne (kabhii) guzari hogi. jab ham ne subah ki to achcha dekha ke aap hira ki taraf se tashrif la rahe hain, unhon-ne kaha ke ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ham ne aapko gum paya to aap ki talash shuru kar di lekin aap na miley, isliye ham ne wo badtareen raat guzari jo koi qaum (kabhi) guzar sakti hai. is par aap ne farmaya : mere paas jinon ki taraf se dawat dene wala aaya to main iske sath gaya aur maine unke samney Quran ki qirat ki. unhon-ne kaha : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein lekar gaey aur hamein unke nuqooshe-qadam aur unki aag ke nishanat dikhaaey . jinon ne aap se zaad ( khuraak (ka sawal kya to aap ne farmaya : tumharey liye har wo haddi hai jis (ke janwar ( par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho aur tumharey hath lag jaey, (is par laga hua) gosht jitna zyada se zyada ho aur (har narm qadmon waley oont aur katey sumon waale) janwar ki leed tumharey janwaron ka chaara hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( insanon se) farmaya : tum un donon chizon se istinja na kya karo kyonke ye donon ( Deen mein) tumharey bhaiyon ( jinon aur unke janwaron (ka khana hain."
1008,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne Dawud se isi sanad ke sath ( وآثار نيرانهم) (unki aag ke nishanat) tak bayan kya. Shabi ne kaha : jinon ne aap se khuraak ka sawal kya aur wo jazeera ke jinon mein se they. . . hadis ke aakhiri hissey tak jo Shabi ka qaul hai, Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis se alag hai."
1009,Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Dawud se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( وآثار نيرانهم) tak riwayat kya aur baad wala hissey bayan nahi kya.
1010,"(Shabi ke bajaey) Ibrahim (Nakhai) ne Alqama se aur unhon-ne Abdullah se riwayat ki, kaha : main 'Lailatul-Jin' ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath na tha aur meri khahish thi ke main aap ke sath hota."
1011,"Ma'n (معن) (bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah-bin-Masood hazli) se riwayat hai, kaha : maine apne walid se suna, kaha : maine Masruq se puchha : jis raat jinon ne kaan laga kar (Quran) suna, uski itlaa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kis ne di? unhon-ne kaha : mujhey tumharey walid (ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bataya ke aapko un jinon ki itlaa aik darakht ne di thi. (ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka mojza tha.)"
1012,"Hajjaj Sawwaf ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-abi-Qatada aur abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein Namaz padhatey to Zohar aur Asr ki pehli 2 rakaton mein sura Fatiha aur 2 soortein (har rakaat mein Fatiha ke baad aik sura ( padhtey aur kabhi kabhaar hamein koi aayat suna detey. Zohar ki pehli rakaat lambi kartey aur dusri rakaat mukhtasar kartey aur subah ki Namaz mein bhi aisa hi kartey."
1013,"(Hajjaj ke bajaey) Hammam aur Aban bin Yazeed ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-abi-Qatada se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar aur Asr ki pehli 2 rakaton mein (se har rakaat mein) sura Fatiha aur aik sura padhtey aur kabhi kabhaar hamein bhi koi aayat suna detey aur aakhiri 2 rakaton mein sura Fatiha padha kartey they."
1014,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne Hushaim se, unhon-ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Waleed bin Muslim se, unhon-ne abu siddeeq (Naji) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Zohar aur Asr main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qiyam ka andaza lagaatey they, to ham ne Zohar ki pehli 2 rakaton mein qiyam ka andaza Sura Sajda ki qirat ke baqadr lagaya aur uski aakhiri 2 rakaton ke qiyam ka andaza us se aadhey ke baqadr lagaya aur ham ne Asr ki pehli 2 rakaton ke qiyam ka andaza lagaya ke wo Zohar ki aakhiri 2 rakaton ke barabar tha aur Asr ki aakhiri 2 rakaton ka qiyam us se aadha tha. Imam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke ustad abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne apni riwayat mein Sura Sajda (ka naam ( zikr nahi kya, unhon-ne kaha : tees aayaton ke jitna."
1015,abu-Awana ne Mansoor se baqi bachi pichhli sanad se Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz mein pehli 2 rakaton mein se har rakaat mein tees aayaton ke baqadr qirat farmatey they aur aakhiri 2 mein pandarah aayaton ke baqadr ya ye kaha is (pehli 2) se nisf aur Asr ki pehli 2 rakaton mein se har rakaat mein pandarah aayaton ke barabar aur aakhiri 2 mein us se nisf .
1016,"Hushaim ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Kufa walon ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ki shikayat ki aur (is mein) unki Namaz ka bhi zikr kya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki taraf paigham bheja , wo aaey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se, Kufa walon ne unki Namaz par jo aetraz kya tha, iska tazkira kya, to unhon-ne kaha : yaqinan main unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ki tarah Namaz padhata hun, usmein kami nahi karta. mein unhein pehli 2 rakatein lambi padhata hun aur aakhiri 2 mein kami karta hun. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aey Abu-Ishaq ! aap ke barey mein guman ( bhi) yahi hai."
1017,Hushaim ke bajaey) Jarir ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki.
1018,"Shoba ne abu-Aaun se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : logon ne aap ki har cheez yahan tak ke Namaz ki bhi shikayat ki hai. Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main (ye kehta hun ke mein) pehli 2 rakaton main ( qiyam ko) tool deta hun aur aakhiri 2 rakaton mein kami karta hun, maine jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhi thi, usmein koi kotahi nahi karta. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap ke barey mein yahi guman hai ya aap ke barey mein mera guman yahi hai."
1019,"Misar ne Abdul-Malik (bin Umair) aur abu Aun se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se unki hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki aur is mein ye izafa kya hai ke Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : badwi mujhey Namaz sikhaaengey? (maine to khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Namaz seekhi hai.)"
1020,"Atiya bin Qais ne Qaza se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Zohar ki Namaz ki iqamat kahi jati aur koi janey wala Baqee jata, apni zarurat se farigh ho kar wuzu karta, phir (masjid mein) aata aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey lamba karne ki wjah se abhi pehli rakaat mein hotey."
1021,"Rabee ne kaha : Qaza ne mujhey hadis sunai, kaha : main Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, unke paas (istifaadey ke liye) kasarat se log maujood they. jab ye log unse ( rukhsat ho kar) muntashir ho gaey to maine kaha : main aap se un chizon ke barey mein sawal nahi karunga jinke barey mein log aap se sawal kar rahe they. maine kaha : main aap se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein poochhta hun. unhon-ne kaha : is sawal mein terey liye bhalai nahi hai (kyonke tum Namaz padhaney waley hukmaranon ke peechhey aisi Namaz nahi padh sakogey) unhon-ne unke samney dobara apna masla pesh kya to Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Zohar ki Namaz khadi ki jati aur ham mein se koi Baqee ki taraf jaata, apni zarurat poori karta, phir apne ghar aa kar wuzu karta, iske baad wapas masjid mein aata to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi pehli rakaat mein hotey they."
1022,"Hajjaj-bin Muhammad ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, neez Abdur-Razzaq ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : ibne-Juraij ne hamein bataya , kaha : maine Muhammad-bin Ibad bin Jafar se suna, keh rahe they : mujhey abu-Salma bin Sufiyan , Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas aur Abdullah-bin Musaiyab se aabidi ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey huey khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Makka mein subah ki Namaz padhai to sura mominoon ki qirat shuru ki yahan tak ke Musa aur Harun (Alaihissalam) ka zikr aaya ya Esa (Alaihissalam) ka zikr aaya ( Muhammad-bin Ibad ko shak hai ya rawiyon ne iske samney ( bayan kartey huey) ikhtilaf kya hai) (is waqt) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khansi aaney lagi to aap rukoo mein chaley gaey. Abdullah-bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) bhi us Namaz mein maujood they. Abdur-Razzaq ki riwayat mein hai : aap ne qirat khatm kar di aur rukoo mein chaley gaey aur unki hadis main ( rawi ka naam ( Abdullah ibne- Amr hai, aagey ibne- Aas nahi kaha"
1023,Hazrat Amr-bin-Hurais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko fajr ki Namaz main (واليل إذا عسعس) (qasam hai raat ki ! jab wo janey lagti hai) padhtey huey suna
1024,"abu-Awana ne Ziyad bin Ilaqa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Qutba bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Namaz padhi aur hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai , aap ne ( ق والقرآن المجيد ( padhi yahan tak ke aap ne (والنخل باسقت) (aur kajhoor ke buland w bula darakht ( padha to main us aayat ko baar-baar ( zahan mein) dohraney laga aur aap ne jo kaha mujhey us (ke mafhoom (ka pata na chala ."
1025,( abu-Awana ke bajaey) Sharik aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Ziyad bin Ilaqa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Qutba bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne fajr ki Namaz main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ( والنخل باسقت لها طلع نضيد ) (aur kajhoor ke buland w bula darakht ( paida kiye ( jinke khoshey teh b teh hain) ki qirat kartey huey suna
1026,"( abu-Awana , Sharik aur ibne-Uena ke bajaey) Shoba ne Ziyad bin Ilaqa se aur unhon-ne apne chacha (Hazrat Qutba bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath subah ki Namaz padhi to aap ne pehli rakaat main ( والنخل باسقت لها طلع نضيد) padha aur kabhi-kabhi ( yahi baat sunatey huey) kaha : Sura Qaf padhi."
1027,"Zayda ne kaha : hamein Samak-bin-Harab ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki Namaz main ( ق والقرآن المجيد ( padha kartey they, iske bawajud aap ki Namaz halki thi."
1028,"( Zayda ke bajaey) Zuhair ne Samak se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne jawab diya : aap halki Namaz padhatey they aur un logon ki tarah Namaz nahi padhatey they. aur) Samak ne) kaha : mujhey unhon ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ ( ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki subah ki Namaz main ( ق والقرآن (aur ( tawaalat mein) us jaisi soortein padha kartey they"
1029,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz main ( واليل اذا يغشى ( (aur raat ki qism jab chhaa jaey) padhtey , Asr mein bhi aisi hi koi sura padhtey aur fajr ki Namaz mein us se lambi ( sura padhtey .)"
1030,"Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Samak se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zohar ki Namaz main ( سبح اسم ربك الأعلى‏ ( (apne parwardigar ke oonchey naam ki tasbeeh kar) padhtey aur subah ki Namaz mein us se lambi qirat kartey they."
1031,( Sulaiman ( Taimi ne abu Minhal se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah ki Namaz mein sath se so (60-100) aayatein tak padha kartey they.
1032,"( Taimi ke bajaey) Khalid Haza ne abu Minhal se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki Namaz mein sath se so (60-100) tak aayatein padha kartey they."
1033,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : umme-Fazal binte- Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey (Mursalat urfa) padhtey huey suna to kehney lagein : betaa ! tum ne ye sura padh kar mujhey yad kara diya ke be-shak ye aakhiri sura hai jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maghrib ki Namaz mein tilawat kartey huey suni."
1034,"(Imam Malik ke bajaey) Sufiyan (bin Uena ( , Yunus , Mamar aur Saleh ne Zohri se usi pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur Saleh ki hadis mein ye izafa hai : phir aap ne iske baad Namaz nahi padhai yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne aapko apne paas bula liya."
1035,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri) se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Juber bin Mut-im se aur unhon-ne apne walid (Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke maine maghrib ki Namaz main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sura taur padhtey huey suna."
1036,"Sufiyan, Yunus aur Mamar ne apni apni sanad se Zohri se usi pichhli sanad ke sath us jaisi riwayat bayan ki."
1037,"Shoba ne Adi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein they, aap ne isha ki Namaz padhai to uski aik rakat main ( والتين والزيتون ( padhi."
1038,"( Shoba ke bajaey) Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Adii-bin Sabit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath isha ki Namaz padhi to aap ne ( والتين والزيتون ( ki qirat ki."
1039,"( Shoba aur Yahya ke bajaey) Misar ne Adii-bin Sabit se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isha ki Namaz main ( والتين والزيتون ( ki qirat kartey huey suna, maine kisi ko nahi suna jiski awaz aap se zyada achi ho."
1040,"Sufiyan ne Amr se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padha kartey they, phir aa kar apne qabeeley ki (masjid mein) imamat karatey , aik raat unhon-ne isha ki Namaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhi, phir apni qaum ke paas aaey, unki imamat ki aur) sura Fatiha ke baad) sura Baqra padhni shuru kar di. aik shakhs alag ho gaya, (namaz se) salam phera , phir akeley Namaz padhi aur chala gaya to logon ne us se kaha : aey falan ! kya to munafiq ho gaya hai? us ne jawab diya : Allah ki qism ! nahi, mein zaroor Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar aapko is mamley se aagah karunga, chunanche wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! ham un oonton waley hain jo pani dhotey hain, din bhar kaam kartey hain aur Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne isha ki Namaz aap ke sath padhi, phir aa kar sura Baqra ke sath Namaz shuru kar di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye sun kar) Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf rukh kya aur farmaya : aey Muaz ! kya logon ko fitney mein mubtala karne waley ho? falan sura padha karo aur falan sura padha karo. Sufiyan ne kaha : maine Amr se kaha : abu-Zubair ne hamein Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke aap ne farmaya : ( والشمس وضحها ( ) والضحى ( , ( واليل إذا يغشى (aur ( سبح اسم ربك الأعلى‏ ( padha karo aur Amr ne kaha is jaisi ( soortein padha karo. ("
1041,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Muaz-bin-Jabal Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne sathiyon ko isha ki Namaz padhai aur is mein lambi qirat ki. ham mein se aik aadmi nikla aur alag Namaz padh li. Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko iske barey mein bataya gaya to unhon-ne kaha : wo munafiq hai. jab us aadmi tak ye baat pahunchi to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aapko bataya ke Muaz ne kya kaha, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : aey Muaz ! kya tum fitna dalney waley banna chahtey ho? jab logon ki imamat karao to ( والشمس وضحها , سبح اسم ربك الأعلى,  اقرأ باسم ربك الذي خلق  aur ( واليل إذا يغشى ( padha karo."
1042,"Mansoor ne Amr-bin-Dinar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath isha ki Namaz padha kartey they, phir apni qaum mein aa kar yahi Namaz unko padhatey they."
1043,"( Mansoor ke bajaey) Ayub ne Amr-bin-Dinar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath isha ki Namaz padha kartey they, phir apni qaum ki masjid mein aa kar unko Namaz padhatey they."
1044,"Hushaim ne Ismail bin abi Khalid se, unhon-ne Qais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : be-shak main falan aadmi ki wjah se subah ki Namaz se peechhey rehta hun kyonke wo hamein bahut lambi namaz padhata hai. abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain : maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kabhi nahi dekha ke pand w nasihat kartey waqt , aap kabhi us din se zyada ghazab naak huey hun. aap ne farmaya : logo ! tum mein se kuchh ( dusron ko Namaz se) mutnaffar karne waley hain. tum mein se jo bhi logon ki imamat kiraaey wo ikhtisar se kaam ley kyonke iske peechhey boodhey , kamzor aur haajat mand log hotey hain."
1045,"Hushaim , Wakee , Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Sufiyan ne Ismail (bin abi Khalid ( se isi sanad ke sath Hushaim ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
1046,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi fard logon ki imamat kiraaey to wo halki Namaz padhaaey kyonke un ( namaziyon ( mein bachchey , boodhey , kamzor aur bimar bhi hotey hain aur jab akelaa padhey to jaisey chahey padhey ."
1047,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein ye hadisein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne bahut si hadisein bayan kiin aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi logon ka imam baney to wo Namaz (qirat) mein kami karey kyonke logon mein boodhey bhi hotey hain aur unmein kamzor bhi hotey hain aur jab akelaa padhey to apni Namaz jitni chahey lambi kar ley."
1048,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs logon ko Namaz padhaaey to wo (qirat mein) kami karey kyonke logon mein kamzor , bimar aur zarurat mand bhi hotey hain."
1049,"abu-Salma ke bajaey) Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : . . . . usi ki tarah , albatta usmein ( saqeem ( ) bimar ( ki jagah ( kabir ( ) boodha ( kaha hai."
1050,"Musa-bin-Talha ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Usman bin abu-Aas Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : apni qaum ki imamat karao . maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! main apne dil mein kuchh mehsus karta hun. aap ne farmaya : mere qareeb ho jao . aap ne mujhey apne samney bitha liya, phir apni hatheli meri donon chhaatiyon ke darmyan rakhi , iske baad farmaya : rukh phero . iske baad aap ne hatheli meri pusht par mere donon kandhon ke darmyan rakhi , phir farmaya : apni qaum ki imamat karao aur jo logon ka imam baney , wo (qirat mein) kami karey kyonke unmein boodhey hotey hain, unmein bimar hotey hain, unmein kamzor hotey hain aur unmein zarurat mand hotey hain, jab tum mein se koi akelaa Namaz padhey to jaisey chahey padhey ."
1051,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne kaha : Hazrat Usman bin abi-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aakhiri baat jo mere zimmey lagai ye thi : jab tum logon ki imamat karao to unhein Namaz halki padhaao ."
1052,Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz (qirat) mein kami kartey aur mukammal ada kartey they.
1053,Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (sab se zyada ( mukammal sura mein sabse zyada kami ke sath Namaz padhaaney waley they.
1054,Sharik bin-Abdullah abi namr ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine kabhi kisi aisey imam ke peechhey Namaz nahi padhi jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz se zyada halki aur zyada mukammal Namaz padhaaney wala ho.
1055,"Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maa ke sath ( aaey huey) bachchey ka ronaa suntey aur aap Namaz mein hotey to halki sura ya (kaha ( chhoti sura padh letey."
1056,"Qatada ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Namaz shuru karta hun, mera irada lambi Namaz (padhney) ka hota hai, phir bachchey ka ronaa sunta hun to bachchey par maa ke gham ki shiddat ki wjah se (namaz mein) kami kar deta hun."
1057,"Hilal bin abi Humaid ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke maine Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maiyat (sath) main ( padhi janey wali) Namaz ko ghaur se dekha to maine aap ke qiyam, rukoo, rukoo ke baad aetidaal aur aap ke sajdey, donon sajdon ke darmyan jalsey ( baithna (aur aap ke doosrey sajdey aur uske baad salam aur rukh pherney ke darmyan waqfey (kuchh dinon) ko taqriban barabar paya."
1058,"Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha ke ibne- Ashas ke zamaney mein aik shakhs (Hakam ne iska naam liya) Kufa (ke iqtidaar) par qaabiz ho gaya, us ne abu Ubeda bin-Abdullah (bin Masood ( ko hukm diya ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein, wo Namaz padhatey they, jab wo rukoo se sar uthatey to itni der khadey hotey ke main ye dua padh leta : aey Allah ! hamarey rab! hamd terey hi liye hai jis se aasman w zamin bhar jayen aur unke siwa jo cheez to chahey bhar jaey. aey azmat w sana ke sazawar! jo to de usko koi rokney wala nahi aur jo to rok ley usey koi bhi dene wala nahi aur na hi kisi martabey waley ko terey samney iska martaba nafa de sakta hai. (sirf teri rehmat hai jo fayda de sakti hai.) Hakam ne kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se iska zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha : maine Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ( qiyam ( , aap ka rukoo aur jab aap rukoo se sar uthatey , aap ke sajdey aur donon sajdon ke darmyan ( wala baithney (ka waqfa taqriban barabar they. Shoba ne kaha : maine iska zikr Amr-bin-Murra se kya to unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela ko dekha hai, unki Namaz is tarah nahi hoti thi. (wo qaabile-bharosa they. unki riwayat qaabile-bharosa hai chahey wo is par poori tarah amal na kar saktey hon.)"
1059,Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam se hadis bayan ki ke jab Matar bin Najiya Kufa par qaabiz ho gaya to usne abu Ubeda ko hukm diya ke wo logon ko Namaz padhaaein. . aur) poori ( hadis bayan ki.
1060,"Khalaf bin Hisham ne Hammad-bin-Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sabit se aur unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : main tumhen aisi Namaz padhaaney mein kotahi nahi karta, jaisi maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha (ke wo ( hamein padhatey they. Sabit ne kaha : Anas (Raziallahu anhu) aik aisa kaam kya kartey they jo main tumhen kartey huey nahi dekhta . jab wo rukoo se apna sar uthatey to seedhey khadey ho jatey yahan tak ke kehney wala kehta ke wo bhool gaey hain aur jab wo sajde se apna sar uthatey to thahrey rahtey yahan tak ke kehney wala kehta : wo bhool gaey hain."
1061,"Behaz ne Hammad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine kisi ke peechhey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada halki Namaz nahi padhi jo kaamil ho. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz (main arkaan ki tawaalat ( qareeb qareeb thi aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki Namaz bhi qareeb qareeb hoti thi. jab umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ameer muqarrar ( huey to unhon-ne namaze-Fajr (main qirat ( lambi kar di aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey to khadey rahtey yahan tak ke ham kehtey : aap ( shayad sar uthana ( bhool gaey hain, phir sajda kartey aur 2 sajdon ke darmyan baithey rahtey yahan tak ke ham samajhtey (ke shayad (aap bhool gaey hain."
1062,"Zuhair aur abu khaisma ne apni apni sanad ke sath Abu-Ishaq se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Yazeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki aur wo jhoot nahi boltey they ke wo log ( sahaba kiram ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhtey they. jab aap rukoo se apna sar utha letey to main kisi ko na dekhta ke wo apni pusht jhukata ho yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni peshani zamin par rakh detey, iske baad aap ke peechhey waley sajdey mein girtey ."
1063,"Sufiyan ne Abu-Ishaq se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki aur wo jhoot bolney waley na they, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab (سمع الله لمن حمدہ) kehtey to ham mein se koi aik bhi us waqt tak apni pusht na jhukata jab tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajdey mein na chaley jatey, phir ham aap ke baad sajdey mein jatey"
1064,"Maharib bin Disaar ne kaha ke maine Abdullah-bin Yazeed ko member par bayan kartey huey suna, wo keh rahe they : Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein bataya ke wo log ( sahaba kiram ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey they, jab aap rukoo mein chaley jatey to wo rukoo kartey aur jab aap apna sar rukoo se uthatey to aap ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey, ham khadey rahtey yahan tak ke ham aapko dekhtey ke aap ne apna chehra Mubarak zamin par rakh diya hai, phir ham aap ki pairwi kartey ( sajdey mein jatey. ("
1065,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-Numair ne kaha : ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aban wghaira ne hukm se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Lela se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham (namaz mein) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hotey , ham mein se koi aik bhi apni pusht na jhukata yahan tak ke ham aapko dekh letey ke aap sajdey mein ja chukey hain. Zuhair ne kaha : Sufiyan ne hamein bataya ke Kufa ke rawiyon Aban wghaira ne hamein hadis sunai, unhon-ne (حتی نراہ قد سجد) ham dekhtey ke wo sajdey mein ja chukey ke bajaey) (حتی نراہ یسجد ) ( ham unhein sajda kartey dekhtey (ke alfaz kahey."
1066,"Hazrat Amr-bin-Hurais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey fajr ki Namaz padhi to maine aapko ( فلا أقسم بالخنس۝ الجوار الكنس ( main qism khata hun peechhey hatney waale, seedhey chalney , dubak janey waley ( sitaron ( ki padhtey huey suna aur ham mein se koi aadmi apni pusht nahi jhukata tha yahan tak ke aap poori tarah sajdey mein chaley jatey they."
1067,"Aamash ne Ubaid bin Hasan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-abi-Ufa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab rukoo se apni pusht uthatey to kehtey, Allah ne sun li jisne uski hamd ki, aey Allah hamarey rab! terey hi liye tareef w tauseef hai aasman bhar , zamin bhar aur unke siwa jo to chahey uski wusat bhar ."
1068,Shoba ne ubaid-bin Hasan se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Ufa se riwayat ki hai unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dua maanga kartey they aey Allah hamarey rab teri hi tareef hai aasman aur zamin tak aur iske ilawa jahan tak to chahey us cheez ki wusat tak.
1069,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Majza bin-Zaahir se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kar rahe they ke aap farmaya kartey they : aey Allah ! terey liye hai hamd aasman bhar, zamin bhar aur unke siwa jo cheez to chahey uski wusat bhar . aey Allah ! mujhey paak kar de barf ke sath , olon ke sath aur thandey pani ke sath . aey Allah ! mujhey gunahon aur khataaon se is tarah saaf kar de jis tarah safaid kapda mail kuchail se saaf kya jata hai."
1070,Ubaidullah ke walid Muaz Anbari aur Yazid-bin-Harun donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath uper zikr ki gaee riwayat bayan ki. Muaz ki riwayat main ( من الوسخ (ke bajaey) ( من الدرن (aur Yazeed ki riwayat main ( من الدنس (ke alfaz hain ( teenon lafzon ke mana aik hi hain. (
1071,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab rukoo se apna sar uthatey to farmatey : aey hamarey rab! terey hi liye tareef hai aasman bhar, zamin bhar aur unke siwa jo cheez to chahey uski wusat bhar . sana aur azmat ke haq daar ! ( yahi ( sahi tareen baat hai jo banda keh sakta hai aur ham sab terey hi bandey hain. aey Allah ! jo kuchh to inayat farmana chahey, usey koi rok nahi sakta aur jis se to mahroom kar de, wo koi de nahi sakta aur na hi kisi martaba waley ko terey samney iska martaba nafa de sakta hai."
1072,"Hushaim bin Bashir ne bayan kya : hamein Hisham bin Hassan ne Qais-bin-Sad se khabar di, unhon-ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab rukoo se sar uthatey to farmatey : aey Allah , aey hamarey rab! terey hi liye tamam tareef hai aasman aur zamin bhar aur un donon ke darmyan ki wusat bhar aur unki baad jo to chahey uski wusat bhar . aey tareef aur buzurgi ke sazawar ! jo to inayat farmaai usey koi chheen nahi sakta aur jis se to mahroom kar de wo koi de nahi sakta aur na kisi martabey waley ko terey samney iska martaba nafa de sakta hai."
1073,"Hafs ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hisham bin Hassan ne baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un alfaz tak riwayat ki : aur unke baad jo to chahey uski wusat bhar . unhon ( Hafs ( ne aagey ka hissa bayan nahi kya."
1074,"Saeed bin Mansoor , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis bayan ki ke mujhey Sulaiman-bin Suhem ne khabar di, unhon-ne Ibrahim bin-Abdullah-bin Mabad se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( darwazey ka ( parda uthaya (is waqt) log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey saf basta they. aap ne farmaya : logo ! nabwooat ki bashaaraton mein se ab sirf sachey khuwab baqi reh gaey hain jo musalman khud dekhega ya uske liye ( kisi doosrey ko) dikhaya jaeyga khabardaar raho ! bila shubah mujhey rukoo aur sajdey ki haalat mein Quran padhney se mana kya gaya hai, jahan tak rukoo ka talluq hai us main apne rab azz-w-jall ki azmat w badai bayan karo aur jahan tak sajdey ka talluq hai is mein khub dua karo, (ye dua us ( laaiq hai ke tumharey haq mein qabool kar li jaey. Imam Muslim ke asaatza mein se aik ustad abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne hadis bayan kartey huey (mujhey Sulaiman ne khabar di, ke bajaey) Sulaiman se riwayat hai, kaha,"
1075,"Ismail bin Jafar ne Sulaiman se baqi bachi pichhli sanad se Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne parda uthaya , us marz ke aalim mein jis mein aap ka intiqal hua, aap ka sar patti se bandha hua tha, aap ne farmaya : aey Allah ! kya maine paigham pahuncha diya ? teen baar (ye alfaz kahey , phir farmaya : ( nabwooat ki bashaaraton mein se ab sirf sachey khuwab baqi reh gaey hain jo koi nek insan khud dekhega ya uske liye (doosrey ko) dikhaaey jaengey. . . iske baad Ismail ne Sufiyan ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
1076,"ibne-Shahab Zohri ne kaha : mujhey Ibrahim bin-Abdullah-bin Hunain ne hadis sunai ke unke walid ne unse bayan kya, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo aur sajdey mein Quran padhney se mana farmaya."
1077,"Waleed bin Kasir se riwayat hai ke mujhey Ibrahim bin-Abdullah-bin Hunain ne apne walid se bayan kya, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, jab main rukoo ya sajdey mein hun, Quran padhney se roka."
1078,"Zaid-bin-Aslam ne Ibrahim bin-Abdullah-bin Hunain se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rukoo aur sajdey mein) Quran ki) qirat karne se mana kya. main (ye ( nahi kehta : tumhen mana kya. (hazrat Ali ne apne hawale se jo suna wahi bataya . pichhli hadison se waazeh hota hai ke hukm sab ke liye hai.)"
1079,"Dawud bin Qais ne kaha : mujhey Ibrahim bin-Abdullah-bin Hunain ne apne walid , unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke mere Habib (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey is baat se mana farmaya tha ke main rukoo ya sajdey mein Quran padhun."
1080,"Naafe, Yazeed bin abi Habib, Suhak bin Usman, ibne-Ajlan, Usama-bin-Zaid, Muhammad-bin Amr aur Muhammad-bin-Ishaq sab ne mukhtalif sanadon se Ibrahim bin-Abdullah Hunain se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, albatta unmein Suhak aur ibne- Ajlan ne izafa kartey huey kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne mujhey rukoo ki haalat mein Quran ki qirat se rokaa aur unmein se kisi ne apni riwayat main (Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke pichhli riwayaton : 1076 . 1079 mein mazkura (uper zikr) shaagirdon) Zohri, Zaid-bin-Aslam, Waleed bin Kasir aur Dawud bin Qais ki riwayat ki tarah sajdey mein qirat karne se rokney ka zikr nahi kya."
1081,Abdullah-bin Hunain ke aik aur shagird Muhammad-bin Munkadir ne yahi hadis Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki lekin sajdey mein qirat ka zikr nahi kya.
1082,Abdullah-bin Hunain ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : mujhey rukoo ki haalat mein qirat se mana kya gaya hai. is sanad mein Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kya.
1083,"Zakwan ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : banda apne rab ke sabse zyada qareeb us haalat mein hota hai jab wo sajdey mein hota hai, lihaza usmein kasarat se dua karo."
1084,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajdey mein kaha kartey they : Allah ! mere sarey gunah bakhsh de, chhotey bhi aur badey bhi, pehley bhi aur pichhley bhi, khuley bhi aur chhipey bhii."
1085,"Mansoor ne abu zuhaa (Muslim-bin Sabeeh al-Qarshi) se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne rukoo aur sajdey mein kasrat se (ye kalimaat ( kaha kartey they : teri pakeezgi bayan karta hun aey mere Allah ! hamarey rab! teri hamd ke sath , aey mere Allah ! mujhey bakhsh de. aap (ye kalimaat ( Quran Majeed ki taaweel (hukm par amal karney) ke taur par farmaya kartey they."
1086,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Muslim (bin sabeeh se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wafat se pahley kasrat se ye farmatey they : (aey Allah ! ( main teri hamd ke sath teri sataaish karta hun, tujh se bakhshish talab karta hun aur teri taraf rujoo karta hun. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! ye kalimey kya hain jo main dekhti hun ke aap ne ab kehney shuru kar diye hain? aap ne farmaya : mere liye meri ummat mein aik alamat muqarrar kar di gaee hai ke jab main usey dekh loon to ye ( kalimey ( kahun : jab Allah ki Nusrat aur fateh aa pahunchey . . . .) sura ke aakhir tak"
1087,"Mufazzal ne Aamash se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab se aap par ( إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح) utri , us waqt se maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ne jo bhi Namaz padhi usmein ye dua mangi ya ye kaha : aey mere rab! main teri pakeezgi bayan karta hun teri hamd ke sath, aey mere Allah ! mujhey bakhsh de."
1088,"Aamir ( Shabi ( ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kasarat se ye farmaya kartey they : main Allah ki pakeezgi bayan karta hun uski hamd ke sath, main Allah se bakhshish ka talabgaar hun aur usi ki taraf rujoo karta hun. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! main aapko dekhti hun ke aap kasrat se kehtey hain : ( سبحان الله وبحمده ، أستغفر الله وأتوب إليه) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha to aap ne farmaya : mere rab ne mujhey khabar di hai ke main jaldi hi apni ummat mein aik nishani dekhunga aur jab main usko dekh loon to kasrat se kahun : ( سبحان الله وبحمده ، أستغفر الله وأتوب إليه) to (wo nishani) main dekh chuka hun. jab Allah ki nusrat aur fateh aa pahunchey (yani ( fateh Makka aur aap logon ko Allah ke Deen mein jooq dar jooq dakhil hotey dekh lein to apne parwardigar ki hamd ke sath uski pakeezgi bayan karein aur us se bakhshish talab karein bila shubah wo tauba qabool farmanewala hai."
1089,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : maine Ata se puchha : aap rukoo mein kya kehtey hain? unhon-ne kaha : jahan tak ( dua ( (سبحانك وبحمدك ، لا إله إلا أنت) to paak hai) aey Allah ! ( apni hamd ke sath , koi mabude-bar-haq nahi terey siwa ka talluq hai to mujhey ibne- Muleka ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : aik raat maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gum paya to maine ye guman kya ke aap apni kisi (aur ( biwi ke paas chaley gaey hain, maine talash kya, phir aap rukoo ya sajdey mein they, keh rahe they : (سبحانك وبحمدك ، لا إله إلا أنت) maine kaha : aap pe mere maan-baap qurbaan! main aik kaifiyat mein thi aur aap aik aur hi kaifiyat mein they."
1090,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bistar par na paya to aapko tatolney lagi , mera hath aap ke paon ke talwey par pada, us waqt aap sajdey mein they, aap ke donon paon khadey they aur aap keh rahe they : aey Allah ! main teri narazagi se teri raza-mandi ki panah mein aata hun aur teri saza se teri maafi ki panah mein aata hun aur tujh se teri hi panah mein aata hun, main teri sana poori tarah bayan nahi kar sakta, to waisa hi hai jaisey tuney apni tareef khud bayan ki."
1091,"Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Mutarrif bin-Abdullah-bin Shikhkhir se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne rukoo aur sajdey mein (ye kalimaat ( kehtey they : bahut hi zyada paak hai, muqaddas hai farishton aur Rooh ( Jibreel ‌(Alaihissalam) ‌ (ka parwardigar ."
1092,"hamein Abu-Dawud ( Tiyalisi ( ne Shoba se hadis sunai ke Qatada ne kaha : maine Mutarrif bin-Abdullah-bin Shikhkhir se suna. Abu-Dawud ne ( mazeed ( kaha : aur Hisham ne mujhey hadis sunai unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Mutarrif se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis riwayat ki."
1093,"Madaan bin abi Talha Yamari ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to maine kaha : mujhey koi aisa amal bataiye jisey karun to Allah uski wjah se mujhey jannat mein dakhil farma de, ya unhon-ne kaha : maine puchha : jo amal Allah ko sabse zyada mahboob ho, to Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ne khamoshi ikhtiyar farmai (aur meri baat ka koi jawab na diya) phir maine dobara unse sawal kya, unhon-ne khamoshi ikhtiyar kar li, phir maine unse teesri baar yahi sawal kya to unhon-ne kaha : maine yahi sawal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya tha to aap ne farmaya tha : tum Allah ke huzoor kasarat se sajdey kya karo kyonke tum Allah ke liye jo bhi sajda karogey Allah uske nateejey main tumhara darja zaroor buland karega aur tumhara koi gunah maaf kar dega. Madaan ne kaha : phir main abu Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to unse ( yahi ( sawal kya, unhon-ne bhi mujh se wahi kaha jo Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha."
1094,"Hazrat Rabee bin Kab (bin Malik ( Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main ( khidmat ke liye) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ( suffa mein aap ke qareeb (raat guzara karta tha, (jab aap tahajjud ke liye uthtey to ( main wuzu ka pani aur dusri zaruriyat lekar aap ki khidmat mein hazir hota. (eik martaba) aap ne mujhey farmaya : (kuchh) mango. to maine kaha : main aap se ye chahta hun ke jannat mein bhi aap ki rifaqat naseeb ho. aap ne farmaya : ya iske siwa kuchh aur ? maine kaha : bas yahi . to aap ne farmaya : tum apne mamley mein sajdon ki kasarat se meri madad karo."
1095,"Yahya aur abu Rabee ne hadis bayan ki, Yahya ne kaha : Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein khabar di aur abu Rabee ne kaha : hamein hadis sunai unhon-ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Taaus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya ke aap saat (7) haddiyon ( waley aazaa ( par sajda kya karein aur aapko baalon aur kapdon ko udasney se mana kya gaya. ye Yahya ki hadis hai aur abu Rabe ne kaha : saat (7) haddiyon (waley aazaa) par sajda karne ka hukm diya gaya aur apne baalon aur apne kapdon ko udasney se mana kya gaya ( saat (7) aazaa se) donon hatheliyan , donon ghutney , donon qadam aur peshani ( murad hain. ("
1096,"Shoba ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Taaus aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya ke main saat (7) haddiyon ( waley aazaa ( par sajda karun aur ye ke main (namaz mein) na kapda udsoon aur na baal ."
1097,Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne ( Abdullah (bin Taaus se aur unhon-ne apne walid ke hawale se Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm diya gaya ke saat (7) ( aazaa ( par sajda karein aur baalon ko aur kapdon ko udasney se roka gaya hai.
1098,"Wuhaib ne Abdullah-bin Taaus se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne (apne walid) Taaus se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey saat (7) haddiyon : peshani , aur) sath hi (aap ne apne hath se apni naak ki taraf ishara kya, donon hathon , donon taangon ( ghutnon (aur donon paon ke kinaron par sajda karne ka hukm diya gaya hai aur ye ke ham (namaz padhtey huey) kapdon aur baalon ko na udsein ."
1099,"ibne-Juraij ne Abdullah-bin Taaus se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main saat (7) ( aazaa ( par sajda karun baalon aur kapdon ko ikattha na karun ( sajda ( peshani aur naak , donon hathon , donon ghutnon aur donon paon par) karun. ("
1100,"Hazrat Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jab banda sajda karta hai to iske sath saat (7) aas-paas ( kinarey ya aazaa) iska chehra , uski donon hatheliyan , iske donon ghutney aur uske donon qadam sajda kartey hain."
1101,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris (bin Nofal (Raziallahu anhu) bin abdul-Muttalib ( ko Namaz padhtey dekha, unke sar par peechhey se baalon ka juda bana hua tha, Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar usko kholney lagey, jab ibne-Haaris ne salam phera to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur kaha : mere sar ke sath aap ka kya mamla hai) mere baal kyon kholey ? ( unhon-ne jawab diya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : is tarah ( juda baandh kar) Namaz padhney waley ki misal us insan ki tarah hai jo us haal mein Namaz padhta hai ke uski mashkein kasi hui hon."
1102,"Wakee ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sajdey mein aetidal ikhtiyar karo aur koi shakhs is tarah apne baazu ( zamin par) na bichhaaey jis tarah kutta bichhata hai."
1103,Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki hai. ibne- Jafar ki riwayat mein hai : koi shakhs takalluf karke apne baazu is tarah na bichhaaey jis tarah kutta bichhata hai.
1104,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum sajda karo to apni hatheliyan (zameen par) rakho aur apni kohniyan uper uthao"
1105,"Bakr bin Muzar ne Jafar bin Rabeea se, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Maalik se, jo ibne- Buhaina (Raziallahu anhu) hain, riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz padhtey to apne hathon ko achi tarah khol detey (apne pahluon se alag kar letey they) yahan tak ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi zahir ho jati thi."
1106,Amr-bin-Haris aur Lais-bin-Sad donon ne Jafar bin Rabeea se isi sanad ke sath (mazkura (uper zikr) hadis) bayan ki. Amr-bin-Haris ki riwayat mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab sajda farmatey to sajdey mein apne bazu (is tarah) phaila letey yahan tak ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi nazar aa jati aur Leis ki riwayat mein hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab sajda kartey to apne hath baghlon se juda rakhtey yahan tak ke main aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekh leta .
1107,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Asamm se, unhon-ne apne chacha Yazeed bin Asamm se, unhon-ne Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda kartey to bakri ka bachcha agar aap ke donon hathon ke darmyan se guzarna chahta to guzar sakta tha."
1108,"Marwan bin Muawiya fazari ne hamein khabar di, kaha : Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Asamm ne Yazeed bin Asamm se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne unhein khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab sajda kartey to apne hathon ke darmyan fasla kartey, unka matlab tha unhein phaila letey yahan tak ke peechhey se aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhi ja sakti thi aur jab baithtey to baain raan par itminan se baithtey."
1109,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Jafar bin Burqan ne Yazeed bin Asamm se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Memuna binte- Haris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab sajda kartey to ( donon hathon ko pahluon se) door rakhtey yahan tak ke jo aap ke peechhey hota wo aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekh sakta tha. Wakee ne kaha : ( wazah se) murad baghlon ki safedi hai."
1110,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abu-Khalid Ahmar ne Husain muallim se hadis sunai, neez Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : (alfaz unhi ke hain) , hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne khabar di, kaha : hamein Husain muallim ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Budail bin Maisra se, unhon-ne abu Jauza se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ki shuruat takbeer se aur qirat ki shuruat ( الحمد لله رب العالمين ( se kartey aur jab rukoo kartey to apna sar na pusht se uncha kartey aur na usey nichey kartey balke darmyan mein rakhtey aur jab rukoo se apna sar uthatey to sajdey mein na jatey yahan tak ke seedhey khadey ho jatey aur jab sajde se apna sar uthatey to ( doosra ( sajda na kartey yahan tak ke seedhey baith jatey aur har 2 rakaton ke baad التحیات padhtey aur apna bayan paon bichhaa letey aur dayan paon khada rakhtey aur shaitan ki tarah ( donon pindliyaan khadi karke ( pichhley hissey par baithney se mana farmatey aur is se bhi mana farmatey ke insan apne bazu is tarah bichha de jis tarah darinda bichhata hai, aur Namaz ka ikhtitaam salam se kartey aur ibne-Numair ki abu-Khalid se riwayat main ( Aqba الشیطان (ke bajaey) ( aqab الشیطان ( hai) mana aik hi hai.)"
1111,"abu-Ahwas ne Samak (bin Harab ( se, unhon-ne Musa-bin-Talha se aur unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi apne samney paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ke barabar koi cheez rakh ley to Namaz padhta rahe aur us se aagey se guzarney waley ki parwaa na kare."
1112,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne hadis bayan ki, Ishaq ne kaha : Umar-bin Ubaid Tanafisi ne hamein khabar di aur ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein hadis sunai, , unhon-ne Samak se, unhon-ne Musa-bin-Talha se aur unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Namaz padh rahe hotey aur jaandaar hamarey samney guzartey ham ne iska tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi shakhs ke aagey paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ke barabar koi cheez ho to phir jo cheez bhi iske samney se guzregi usey iska koi nuqsan nahi. ibne-Numair ne, phir jo cheez bhi iske samney se guzregi , ke bajaey to jo koi bhi iske samney se guzregi usey iska koi nuqsan nahi, ke alfaz bayan kiye."
1113,"Saeed bin abi-Ayub ne abu Aswad se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se namazi ke sutrey ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap ne farmaya : paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ke misl ho."
1114,"Hewa ne abu Aswad Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jange-Tabook mein namazi ke sutrey ke barey mein sawal kya gaya to aap ne farmaya : paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ki tarah ho."
1115,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eid ke din nikaltey to neze ka hukm detey, wo aap ke aagey gaad diya jata, aap uski taraf rukh karke Namaz padhtey aur log aap ke peechhey hotey, safar mein bhi aap aisa hi kartey, is bina par hukkaam ne us (neza gaadney) ko apna liya hai."
1116,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne aur ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis sunai aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) neza gaadtey aur uski taraf rukh karke Namaz padhtey . Imam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke ustad ibne-Numair ne ( يركز (aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne ( يغرز (ka lafz istemal kya ( donon ke mana hain : aap gaadtey they. (aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ki riwayat mein ye izafa hai : Ubaidullah ne kaha is ( anza ( se murad ( harba ( ) barchhi ( hai."
1117,"Motamir bin Sulaiman ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( b-waqt zarurat ( apni sawari ko samney karke ( bitha letey aur) uski taraf ( munh karke ( Namaz padh letey"
1118,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein abu-Khalid Ahmar ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kabhi kabhi) apni sawari ko samney rakhtey huey Namaz padh letey they. aur) Muhammad (bin Numer ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne oont ko samney rakhtey huey ( qibla ru ho kar) Namaz padhi."
1119,"Sufiyan ne bayan kya : hamein Aun bin abi Juhaifa ne apne walid (Hazrat abu Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu)) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Makka main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, aap Abtah ke maqam par chamdey ke aik surkh khemey main ( thahre huey) they. ( abu Juhaifa ne) kaha : Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke wuzu ka pani lekar bahar aaey ( iske baad jab aap ne wuzu kar liya to ( usmein se kisi ko pani mil gaya aur kisi ne (doosrey se uski ( nami ley li. unhon-ne kaha : phir Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) surkh hulla ( libaas ke uper lamba chogha ( pahney huey nikley, ( aisa lagta hai) jaisey ( aaj bhi) mein aap ki pindliyon ki safedi ko dekh raha hun. aap ne wuzu kya aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne azan kahi , unhon-ne kaha : main bhi unke munh peechhey us taraf aur us taraf rukh karne laga, (jab ( wo (حي على الصلاة) aur (حي على الصلاة) keh rahe they, to unhon-ne daaen baaen rukh kya, kaha : phir aap ke liye neza gaadaa gaya aur aap ne aagey badh kar Zohar ki 2 rakatein ( qasr ( padhaain, aap ke aagey se gadha aur kutta guzarta tha, unhein roka na jata tha, phir aap ne Asr ki 2 rakatein padhaain aur phir Madina wapsi tak musalsal 2 rakatein hi padhatey rahe."
1120,"Umar-bin-abi-Zayda se riwayat hai ke mujhey Aun bin abi Juhaifa ne hadis bayan ki ke unke walid ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chamdey ke surkh khemey mein dekha (kaha : (aur maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha wo aap ke wuzu ka pani bahar ley aaey to maine dekha log us pani ko leney ke liye aik doosrey se sabqat ley janey ki koshish kar rahe hain, jis ko us se kuchh pani mil gaya us ne usko badan par mal liya aur jis ko us se na mila to usne apne sathi ke hath ki nami se nami hasil kar li, phir maine Bilal ko dekha unhon-ne aik neza nikala aur usko gaad diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) surkh hulla pahney huey nikley jo aap ne pindliyon tak uncha kya hua tha, aap ne neze ki taraf rukh karke logon ko 2 rakaat Namaz padhai aur maine logon aur chaupayon ko neze ke samney se guzartey huey dekha."
1121,"abu Umais ne aur Maalik-bin-Mighwal donon ne apni apni sanad se Aun bin abi Juhaifa se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Sufiyan aur Amr bin abi Zayda ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya hai. un ( charon Sufiyan , umr , abu Umais aur Malik ( mein kuchh dusron se zayed alfaz bayan kartey hain. Maalik-bin-Mighwal ki hadis mein hai : jab do-pahar ka waqt hua to Bilal nikley aur Namaz ke liye azan di."
1122,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Hakam se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat abu Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : sakht garmi ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Batha ki taraf nikley, wuzu karke us aalim mein Zohar aur Asr ki 2-2 rakatein padhein aur aap ke samney neza tha. Shoba ne kaha : Aun ne apne walid abu Juhaifa se (riwaayat kartey huey) ye izafa kya ke neze ki dusri taraf se auratein aur gadhey guzar rahe they."
1123,"(Abdur-Rehman) bin Mehdi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, (kaha : ( Shoba ne hamein (Hakam aur Aun ki) donon sanadon ke sath pichhli hadis ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki aur unhon ( ibne- Mehdi ( ne hukm ki hadis mein ye izafa kya : to log aap ke wuzu ke bachchey huey pani mein se (pani) leney lagey."
1124,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main gadhi par Sawar ho kar aaya, un dinon mein bulooghat ke qareeb tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina mein logon ko Namaz padha rahe they, main saf ke samney se guzra aur utar kar gadhi ko charney ke liye chhod diya aur Saf mein dakhil ho gaya to mujhey kisi ne is par nahi toka."
1125,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne khabar di ke unhein Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke wo gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaey jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par Mina mein logon ko Namaz padha rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : gadha saf ke kuchh hissey ke aagey se guzra , phir wo us se utar kar logon ke sath saf mein mil gaey."
1126,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath mazkura (uper zikr) riwayat bayan ki, kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Arfa mein Namaz padha rahe they. (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) apni sawari par Haj kar rahe they. ye waqia unke sath ghaaliban Mina aur Arfa donon maqamat par pesh aaya. us se Sabit hota hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye har jagah sutrey ka ehtimam kya jata tha. ("
1127,Mamar ne bhi Zohri se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki hai aur is mein Mina ya Arfa ka tazkira karne ke bajaey Hijjatul-wada ya fateh Makka ke din ka zikr kya hai.
1128,Abdur-Rehman bin abi Saeed ne (apne walid) Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi Namaz padh raha ho to kisi ko aagey se na guzarney de aur jahan tak mumkin ho usko hataaey agar wo na maaney to us se ladey kyonke wo shaitan hai. ( maqsud ye tha ke logon ko us gunah se har qeemat par bachaya jaey aur Namaz ki hurmat ka ehtimaam kya jaey. (
1129,"ibne- Hilal , yani Humaid ne kaha : aik din main aur mera aik sathi aik hadis ke barey mein muzaakra kar rahe they ke Abu-Saleh Sammaan kehney lagey : main tumhen hadis bayan karta hun jo maine abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se suni aur) unka amal ( jo unse dekha. kaha : aik mauqe par, jab main Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha aur wo Juma ke din kisi cheez ki taraf ( rukh karke ( , jo unhein logon se sutrah muhaiya kar rahi thi, Namaz padh rahe they, itney mein abu Mueet ke khandan ka aik naujawaan aaya, us ne unke aagey se guzarna chaha to unhon-ne usey uske seeney se ( peechhey ( dhakela. us ne nazar daudaai, usey abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney se ( guzarney (ke siwa koi rasta na mila, us ne dobara guzarna chaha to unhon-ne usey pehli baar se zyada shiddat ke sath uske seeney se peechhey dhakela, wo seedha khada ho gaya aur abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura bhala kaha, phir logon ki bheed mein ghusta hua nikal kar Marwan ke samney pahunch gaya aur jo iske sath beeti thi uski shikayat ki, kaha : abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Marwan ke paas pahunch gaey to usne unse kaha : aap ka apne bhatijey ka sath kya mamla hai? wo aa kar aap ki shikayat kar raha hai. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai : jab tum mein se koi logon se kisi cheez ki ot mein Namaz padhey aur koi iske aagey se guzarna chahey to wo usey uske seeney se dhakeley agar wo na maaney to us se ladey kyonke wo yaqinan shaitan hai."
1130,"Ismail bin abi-Fudaik ne Suhak bin Usman se, unhon-ne sadqa bin Yasar se, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi Namaz padh raha ho to kisi ko apne aagey se na guzarney de, agar wo na maaney to us se ladey kyonke uske sath mein uska hamrahi (shaitan) hai."
1131,(ibne-abi-Fudaik ke bajaey) Abu-Bakar Hanfi ne Suhak bin Usman se usi (mazkura (uper zikr) (sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : . . . aagey pichhli hadis ki tarah hai.
1132,"Imam Malik ne abu-Nazar se aur unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki ke Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein abu-Juhaim (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bheja taake unse poochhein ke unhon-ne namazi ke aagey se guzarney waley ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya suna tha? abu-Juhaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar namazi ke aagey se guzarney wala jaan ley ke is par kis qadr (gunah) hai to usey chalis (40) (saal) tak khadey rehna, iske aagey guzarney se behtar (maloom) ho. abu-Nazar ne kaha : mujhey malum nahi, unhon-ne chalis (40) din kaha ya maah ya saal."
1133,Sufiyan ne abu-Nazar Salim se aur unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki ke Zaid-bin-Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) ne (unhein ( abu-Juhaim Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja (taake poochhey (ke aap ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kya farmatey suna. . . . phir ( Sufiyan ne) Malik ki riwayat ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
1134,"Hazrat Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sajdey ki jagah aur diwar ki darmyan bakri guzarney ke barabar fasla tha."
1135,Hammad bin Mas-ada ne Yazeed bin abi Ubaid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo ( Salma (Raziallahu anhu)) koshish karke (masjide-Nabawi mein) us jagah nafli Namaz padhtey jahan musahaf ( rakha hua) tha aur unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi jagah ki koshish farmatey they aur) yahan ( member aur qibley ki diwar ke darmyan bakri ke rastey ke barabar fasla tha.
1136,"Makki (bin Ibrahim ( ne kaha : hamein Yazeed bin abi Ubaid ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Salma (bin Akwaa ( (Raziallahu anhu) us sutoon ke paas Namaz padhney ki justju kartey jo musahaf ke paas tha. maine unse kaha : aey abu Muslim ! main dekhta hun ke aap is sutoon ke paas Namaz padhney ka ehtimaam kartey hain. unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko iske qareeb Namaz padhney ka ehtimaam kartey dekha hai."
1137,"Yunus ne Humaid bin Hilal se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Samit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar ( Ghifari ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi Namaz ke liye khada ho jab iske samney paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ke barabar koi cheez hogi to wo usey sutrah muhaiya karegi, aur jab uske samney paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ke barabar koi cheez na hogi to gadhaa , aurat aur siyah kutta uski Namaz ko kaatengey. maine kaha : aey Abu-Zar ! siyah kuttey ki laal kuttey ya zard kuttey se takhsees kyon hai? unhon-ne kaha : bhatijey ! maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi sawal kya tha jo tum ne mujh se kya hai to aap ne farmaya tha : siyah kutta shaitan hota hai."
1138,"Sulaiman-bin Mughira , Shoba , Jareer, Salam bin abu zayyaal aur Aasim ahwal sab ne Humaid bin Hilal se Yunus ki sanad ke sath uski hadis ki manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki hai."
1139,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aurat, gadhaa aur kutta Namaz tod detey hain aur paalaan ki pichhli lakdi ke barabar koi cheez usey bachati hai."
1140,"Zohri ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko Namaz padhtey they, main janazey ki tarah aap ke aur qibley ke darmyan chaudai mein leti hoti thi"
1141,"Hisham ne apne walid Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko apni poori Namaz padhtey aur main aap ke aur qibley ke darmyan leti hoti thi aur jab aap witr padhna chahtey, mujhey jaga detey to main bhi witr padh leti."
1142,"Abu-Bakar bin Hafs ne Urwa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : kon si cheez Namaz tod deti hai? to ham ne kaha : aurat aur gadhaa . is par unhon-ne kaha : aurat bura chaupaaya hai ! maine apne aapko dekha hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney chaudai rukh janazey ki tarah leti hoti thi jabke aap Namaz padh rahe they."
1143,"Aamash ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Ibrahim ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aswad se aur Aswad ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki. Aamash ne ( mazeed ( kaha : mujhey Muslim-bin-Sabeeh ne Masruq se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unke samney un chizon ka tazkira kya gaya jo Namaz tod deti hain (yani ( kutta, gadhaa aur aurat . to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : tum ne hamein gadhon aur kutton ke mushabeh (similar) bana diya hai ! Allah ki qism ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is haal mein Namaz padhtey dekha ke main charpaai par aap ke aur qibley ke darmyan leti hoti thi, mujhey zarurat pesh aati to main baith kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef dena pasand na karti , isliye main us ( charpaai ya bistar) ke paayon ( wali jagah ki taraf ( se khisak jati."
1144,"Mansoor ne Ibrahim ( Nakhai ( se, unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne farmaya : tum ne hamein kutton aur gadhon ke barabar kar diya hai, halanke maine apne aapko (is tarah) dekha hai ke main charpaai par leti hoti thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif latey aur charpai ke beech mein khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey , main aap ke samney hona pasand na karti , isliye main char paai ke paayon ki taraf se khisakti yahan tak ke apne lihaf se nikal jati."
1145,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney so jati aur mere paon aap ke qibley ( waley hissey ( mein hotey , jab aap sajda kartey to ( paon par hath laga kar) mujhey ishara kar detey to main apne donon paon suked leti aur jab aap khadey ho jatey to main unko phaila leti . unhon ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : ghar un dinon aisey they ke unmein charagh nahi hotey they."
1146,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey aur main haiz ki haalat mein aap ke samney hoti, kabhi-kabhi aap sajda kartey to aap ka kapda mujh se lag raha hota."
1147,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko Namaz padhtey aur main haiz ki haalat mein aap ke pahlu ki taraf hoti mujh par chadar hoti aur us chadar ka kuchh hissey aap ke pehlu (ki taraf ( se aap par (bhi) hota.
1148,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik saail ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik kapdey mein Namaz padhney ke barey mein sawal kya to aap ne farmaya : kya tum mein se har aik ke paas 2 kapdey hain?"
1149,"Yunus aur Aqeel-bin-Khalid donon ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pichhli hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
1150,"Muhammad-bin Sirin ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pukar kar puchha : kya ham mein se koi shakhs sirf aik kapdey mein Namaz padh sakta hai? to aap ne farmaya : kya tum mein se har aik ke paas 2 kapdey hain?"
1151,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs aik kapdey mein Namaz is tarah na padhey ke iske kandhon par iska koi hissey na ho.
1152,"abu-Usama ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umar-bin abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha, aap usey lapetey huey they aur uske donon kinarey apne kandhon par rakhey huey they."
1153,"Wakee ne Hisham-bin-Urwa ki uper zikr ki gaee sanad se hadis sunai, haan ye farq hai ke usne ( mutwashshiaa ( kaha ( mushtamilan ( na kaha"
1154,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umar-bin abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha, aap ne iske donon kinaron ko adal-badal kar rakha tha, yani daain kinarey ko baain taraf aur baain kinarey ko daain taraf le gaey they."
1155,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Eisa-bin-Hammad ne kaha : hamein Leis ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis sunai unhon-ne abu Amama bin Sahal-bin-Haneef se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umar-bin abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha : aap ne usko lapeta hua tha aur uske donon kinaron ko mukhalif samt mein daala hua tha. Eisaa-bin-Hammaad ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya : apne kandhon par daley huey they."
1156,"Wakee ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne abu-Zubair se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha, aap ne usko patkey ki tarah lapeta hua tha."
1157,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, neez Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki, un donon ( ibne-Numair aur Abdur-Rehman ( ne Sufiyan se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki. aur ibne-Numair ki hadis mein hai, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan hazir hua."
1158,"Amr ne kaha ke abu-Zubair Makki ne mujhey hadis sunai ke unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha, wo usko patkey ki tarah lapetey huey they aur unke paas unke kapdey maujood they aur Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisey kartey dekha hai."
1159,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu Sufiyan se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, mujhey Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan hazir huey, kaha : to maine aapko aik chataai par Namaz padhtey dekha is par aap sajda kartey they aur maine aapko dekha aap aik kapdey mein usko patkey ki tarah lapet kar Namaz padh rahe they."
1160,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : ham se abu-Muawiya ne bayan kya, neez Suwed-bin-Saeed ne kaha : ham se Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne riwayat ki, donon ne Aamash se isi tarah riwayat ki. abu-Kuraib ki riwayat mein hai : aap ne iske donon kinarey apne kandhon par daley huey they. aur Abu-Bakar aur Suwed ki riwayat mein hai : aap usko patkey ki tarah lapetey huey they."
